Umubare w'abandura indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19) uragenda wiyongera cyane mu muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi/Akarere k'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi n'u Bwongereza, 1 Mutarama kugeza 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko ibintu bisa n'ibi bigenda bigenda byiyongera mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitandukana bitewe n'igihugu, kigenda cyihuta cyane mu bihugu byose.
Nk'uko byari bimeze mu Butaliyani, leta, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bigomba kurushaho kwitegura kwakira abarwayi benshi ba COVID-19 bazagomba kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu byumba by'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, havumbuwe icyorezo cya pneumonia cy'ubwoko butamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iyi ndwara ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus 2 y'ubuhumekero bw'indwara ikomeye cyane (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yiswe icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ibihamya kugeza ubu bigaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 barwaye indwara ntoya, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite umusonga, abenshi muri bo bakaba barakira.
Mu barwayi 14% byageze aho COVID-19 igatera izindi ndwara zikomeye zikeneye kuvurirwa mu bitaro, naho abandi 6% bagakira indwara ikomeye ikeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bw'ibanze.
Umubare w'abapfa mu barwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro ugera kuri 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye ibipimo by'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi/akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (UK) maze tugereranya ibipimo n'iby'ubwandu mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone twagereranyije umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwijwe mu bindi bihugu, kandi uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje gukwirakwira ku isi, ni ko gikomeje gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cy'ingwara.
Mu kinyamakuru Eurosurveillance 2020 cyo ku ya 5 Werurwe, Spiteri et al. batangaje Umunyaburayi wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 byemejwe nk'uko bisobanurwa n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS).
Muri EU/EEA, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe n'Ubufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse baturutse Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, mu bihugu 30 by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza (Ubwongereza) hose, hagati y'itariki 31 Ukuboza 2019 na 15 Werurwe 2020 byonyine, habonetse abantu 39,768 n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, mu Butaliyani honyine habonetse abantu 17,750 n'abantu 1,441.
Kubara umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 no kubara umubare w'abanduye
Ku kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no kurwanya indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi ivugururwa buri munsi saa munani. Iyi mibare ihabwa gusa mu bitabo byemewe nka Minisiteri y'Ubuzima y'icyo gihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'uturere, na OMS.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma ibipimo bya COVID-19 mu muryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kubigereranya n'ibipimo by'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'ibisobanuro by'uko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakomeje kwiyongera, twafashe iminsi 14 y'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye, dufatiye ku buryo COVID-19 yagiye igenda mu buryo busanzwe muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Turagaragaza kandi imibare y'ibarura ry'abamaze kwandura muri buri gihugu kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa, ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'amezi 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imyitegurire y'imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ya nyuma mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange ikurikiza imiterere y'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK muri rusange, ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibyongereweho).
Iyi myigaragambyo ahanini yatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'umubare w'abamaze kwandura mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza na byo byerekanye ko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 buzamuka mu buryo nk'ubwo (Ibisobanuro by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'I Burayi na Areeya y'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ayo makuru agaragaza ko kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'u Bwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye ungana cyangwa uri munsi y'uwa Italy mu byumweru bitatu bishize.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bavugwa uri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu by'ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EAE no mu Bwongereza.
Uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongeye mu bihugu byose, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cy'iyi ndwara cyatangiye kwiyongera ku kigero kimwe.
Ibi birimo n'ubwo ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibyiciro bitandukanye by'ibizamini, impinduka z'ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange, n'ubushobozi bwo gusobanura indwara mu bihugu bitandukanye no gutandukanya uburyo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa COVID-19 kugira ngo byemezwe, harimo no gusuzuma abantu bakurikira.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo mu Butaliyani basobanuye ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe muri ako karere byageze ku bushobozi bwabyo bwose.
Kuri ubu, amakuru y'abanduye COVID-19 ku bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo nderabuzima ku rwego rw'ibihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EAA ni 6% na 1% by'abanduye gusa (amakuru ntiyerekanwe).
Ariko, amakuru agomba gukusanywa mu buryo bw'uburyo kugira ngo yongereho amakuru y'ubugenzuzi bw'ubu burwayi yibanda ku mibare y'abamaze kwandura n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-2011 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari ubwiyongere bw'ibitanda byo mu bitaro by'indembe n'ibyo mu bitaro by'indembe, buri muntu ku bantu 100.000, mu Budage ni 29,2 naho mu Bufaransa ni 4,2.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite amikoro menshi cyangwa make ugereranije n'u Butaliyani (12,5 ibitanda by'indembe n'ibitaro byo mu bitaro ku baturage 100.000 mu 2010-2011).
Imigereranyo y'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi ku bijyanye n'ubwiganze bw'ibitanda byo kwa muganga, hagendewe ku bipimo by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bitaro by'indembe buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi/EEA na UK, hagendewe ku ngaruka >90% z'ibitanda byo kwa muganga, byatanzwe mu itegurwa rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ry'ibyago rya ECDC kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bashyizwe mu turere tw'ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe bikunze kwita ku baturage bafite serivisi z'uturere runaka, amakuru ku barwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe yagombye gutangwa ku rwego rw'Ibarura ry'Akarere 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'imiterere y'ibindi bihugu byerekana ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye vuba cyane mu Burayi bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza.
Ni yo mpamvu ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bigomba kwitegura ko hashobora kubaho ihuriro ry'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 no kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu byumba by'indembe, nk'uko byagenze mu duce twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ry'ibyago ryihuse rya ECDC riheruka, uburyo bwihuse, burangwa no kugenzura no gusesengura ibintu ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, aho umuntu yavuye ku buryo bwo kwirinda agana ku buryo bwo kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abanduye vuba, nk'uko byari byitezwe, bishobora kuba bidaha igihe gihagije abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugira ngo basobanukirwe, kandi bihangane n'uburyo bukwiriye bwo guhangana mu gihe bitakoreshejwe mbere.
Ibyo bizamini byihuse by'ibyago byashyize ahagaragara ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zigamije kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito cyo kwiyongera mu gihe ibihugu bishobora kongera ingamba zo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ingufu ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Iyo bigenze bityo, ubuvuzi bw'ibindi bihugu bya EU/EEA bushobora guhura n'ikibazo cy'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'indembe mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus y'ibicurane by'ubuhumekero ikomeye 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3.000 no kwandura abarenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bivuze amakuba ku bantu.
Kimwe n'izindi virusi zisa na zo, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaturukaga mu ducurama kandi ikaba yatumaga abantu bagira ibimenyetso bisa n'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Nubwo bimeze bityo, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'umubare w'abahitanwa na yo uri hasi ugereranyije na SARS, ariko ni indwara yanduye cyane kandi igenda ifata abantu bakuze cyane kurusha abakiri bato, ndetse igenda ifata abagabo cyane kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wiyongera cyane w'ibitabo kuri iyi ndwara nshya, iyi ngingo igerageza gutanga isesengura ryihuta kandi ryihuse ry'uru rwego rw'ubushakashatsi bwihuta.
Tugiye kuganira ku by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi bw'indwara, impamvu zitera, virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kuboneza no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, twiringiye ko iri sesengura rizadufasha kurushaho gusobanukirwa no kurwanya iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'Icyi wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose bategetswe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru no mu byumweru byakurikiyeho kubera icyorezo gishya cy'indwara y'icyorezo.
Iyi virusi ni homolog cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003; ku bw'ibyo, iyi virusi yiswe SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara itera yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, ariko cyahise gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze guhitana abantu 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40.000 barasubizwa mu gihugu cyabo naho abagera ku 3.000 barapfa.
OMS yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi w'abantu wa mbere" kandi ko ishobora guteza ibyago bikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yashyiragaho urutonde rw'agakoko gatera COVID-19 kavumbuwe mu barwayi bamwe, hasohotse impapuro zirenga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19, zirimo virusi, icyorezo, impamvu, gusuzuma no kuvura.
Iyi raporo igerageza kwerekana iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu bijyanye n'iki cyiciro gishya cy'ubushakashatsi gikomeje kwiyongera.
Mu bushobozi bwacu, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS ndetse n'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, 2012).
Nanone, turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda no gupima indwara, tunarebe n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi bitaraba.
Mu buryo bw'imigenzo, CoVs zifatwa nk'indwara zidakunda kwica abantu, cyane cyane izatera 15% by'ibicurane 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na CoVs zifite ubukana bw'indwara nyinshi ku bantu inshuro ebyiri, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, buri imwe muri zo ikaba yaratumye haduka icyorezo cyatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, maze bidatinze gikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi, abantu benshi bahasiga ubuzima.
Niyo mpamvu COVID-19 ari icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nkuko bigaragara ku Gishushanyo cya 1.1, icyorezo cy'ibicurane cy'inkomoko itazwi cyavuzwe bwa mbere muri Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 muri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abashinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, havumbuwe uko virusi ya CoV yagiye ikurikirana.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, habonetse umuntu wa mbere w'umurwayi wahitanywe n'icyorezo cya Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyahise cyibasira imigi, intara n'ibihugu by'abaturanyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, ubwandu bw'abatanga ubuvuzi bw'ubuzima bwaravuzwe, byerekana ko umuntu ashobora kwanduzanya n'undi muntu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu mujyi wa Wuhan hashyizweho gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi imodoka zose zitwara abantu ku giti cyabo zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere ku cyorezo bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 gusa ni bo bahuye n'isoko rya Wuhan ry'ibiribwa by'inyanja, aho byemezwa ko ubwandu buturutse ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'indwara y'uburwayi ku isi.
Igihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyi ndwara yari yaramaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo cya 2).2).
Kubera ko iki cyorezo kiri mu nzira yo gukwirakwira vuba, umubare w'abantu bazakira n'uko kizaba gikomeye biracyari guhagarikwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, inyigo y'ibigo by'ubuvuzi by'indwara 8.866 harimo abantu 4.021 bagaragaweho COVID-19, yatanze ishusho y'icyorezo ikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yandurira abantu mu myaka yose, ariko cyane cyane hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abanduye bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 50, bake cyane ni abari munsi y'imyaka 20, naho 14 gusa ni abari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduza cyane abagabo (0.31/100.000) kurusha abagore (0.27/100.000).
COVID-19 yibasiye udusumba, cyane cyane mu turere two mu ntara ya Hubei.
COVID-19 itwara iminsi igera kuri 5 (2-9) kuva igihe umuntu ayanduye kugeza igihe agaragaye.
Ikiruhuko cy'iminsi 4,8 (3,0-7,2) ni cyo gisanzwe.
Igihe cyo kuva ku gitereko kugeza ku rupfu ni 9.5 (4,8-13) w'iminsi.
Igishushanyo cy'ibanze cyo kubyara (R0) ni 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05) naho R0 ni 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wariyongereye cyane mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, bitewe n'igihe cyo gutwara abantu benshi mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'Igihembwe mu Bushinwa.
Umubare w'abapfuye ku barwayi bafite ubwandu bw'indwara yemewe ni 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%) naho umubare w'abapfuye ku barwayi bose ni 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Impamvu eshatu z'ingenzi zitera COVID-19 ni igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (≥60), n'indwara y'igifu ikabije.
CoV ni ubwoko bw'indwara zikomeye z'uruvange rw'indwara zikunze kuba mu bwoko bwa virusi, zirimo n'uruvange rw'imiterere ya RNA.
CoVs zishobora kugabanywamo amoko ane, ari yo alpha, beta, gamma na delta, aho alpha- na beta-CoVs zizwiho kwanduza abantu.
Glycoprotein z'igihimba cyangwa spike (S) z'umwenda zihuza n'imiterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo, angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE 2) na dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hanyuma habaho ihuriro ry'urwagashya.
Igikoresho cya virusi cya RNA cyoherezwa muri sitoplasme; nyuma yo gusubiramo igikoresho cya virusi, RNA ya genome iherekejwe na glycoprotein y'umwimerere na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid ihindura vesicle irimo virion, nyuma ijya guhuza na plasma membrane kugirango ivane virusi.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mutarama 2020, havumbuwe ku nshuro ya mbere urutonde rwa genome za SARS-CoV-2.
SARS-CoV-2 ni beta-CoV y'ubwoko bushya ifite umurongo ndangakamere ungana na 99,98% mu bipimo 10 byafashwe; ibipimo byakuwe mu gace k'icyorezo, ku isoko ry'ibiribwa by'inyanja rya Huanan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ku bijyanye na jenoside, SARS-CoV-2 isa cyane na SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Binyuze muri mikorosikopi ya elegitoronike, SARS-CoV-2 y'udupfunyika twavumbuwe mu gice cy'ubuhumekero bw'umuntu buto cyane.
ACE2 y'abantu yagaragaye ko ari yo ikira SARS-CoV-2 kimwe na SARS-CoV.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, poroteyine ya S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifatanya n'umuntu ACE2 ku buryo budafite imbaraga cyane kurusha poroteyine ya S ya SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bihuye n'uko SARS-CoV-2 itera indwara mu buryo budafite ingaruka zikomeye nk'iz'indwara ya SARS-CoV ku barwayi.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kandi gukora poroteyine ngufi nshya ihindurwa na orf3b na poroteyine ihindurwa na orf8.
Poroteyine ya SARS-CoV-2 orf3b ishobora kugira uruhare mu ndwara zanduza virusi no mu kubuza IFNβ kugaragaza; ariko, orf8 nta hantu na hamwe ifite ikoranabuhanga cyangwa impamvu izwi.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al. batangaje ko ACE2 yuzuye ya muntu-EM-EM ifite imiterere ya 2.9 Å mu kigo hamwe na B0AT1 amino acid transporter.
Basanze ko iyo miryango ifite imiterere y'inyuguti ifunguye n'ifunguye, ihurijwe hamwe ikagira imiterere y'inyuguti, kandi ko ACE2-B0AT1 ishobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, ibyo bikaba ari byo bigaragaza ko hari CoV ishobora kwanduza umuntu.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba icyorezo mu gupima imiti igabanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Inzu y'amavuko n'ibanga
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV bizwi ko byakomotse ku ducurama kandi buri kimwe muri byo cyanduzwa abantu n'ibinyugunyugu na ngamiya.
Binyuze mu kugereranya imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi CoVs, bivugwa ko ari yo nyirabayazana wa SARS-CoV-2 kuko virusi nshya ifite 96% by'ubumwe n'izindi CoVs ebyiri zisa na SARS zo mu bwoko bwa SARS zo mu bwoko bw'inguge, ari zo bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Ariko kandi, nta wamenya neza ubwoko bw'imiti virusi ishobora kwanduriraho abantu, ndetse n'inzira ishobora kwanduzaho iracyari amayobera.
Ji, et al. batanze igitekerezo cy'uko inzoka ari yo ikwirakwiza virusi iva mu nguge ijya mu bantu, ikoresheje gukorakorana kw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa S.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi, abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa, batanze igitekerezo cy'uko ingona, inyamaswa y'inzitiramibu ifite umunwa muremure irya inzoka ikunda gukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa, ishobora kuba inyamaswa y'ingona ya SARS-CoV-2 ishingiye kuri 99% by'ubwuzu bumwe bwa CoV iboneka mu ngona na SARS-CoV-2.
Nyamara, 1% by'ubwisanzure mu bumenyi bw'ibinyabuzima, ni itandukaniro rinini; ku bw'ibyo, nta bimenyetso bifatika by'ibimenyetso bifatika by'ubwo bushakashatsi biriho (Igishushanyo cya 3).
Imiterere ya physico-chimie ya SARS-CoV-2 iracyari izwi.
In vitro, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kumara amasaha 48 mu karere gakakaye, zikamara iminsi 5 ku bushyuhe bwa 20 °C no ku bushyuhe bwa 40%-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite imiterere nk'iyo.
Byavuzwe ko SARS-CoV-2 ifata cyane urumuri rwa ultraviolet n'ubushyuhe ku kigero cya 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; ether, 75% ya ethanol, umuti wica imibu urimo chlorine, aside ya peracetate, chloroform n'indi miti ivura ibinure, ariko itarimo chlorhexidine, byagize ingaruka nziza mu guhagarika virusi.
Muri rusange, abantu bose nta rukingo bafite kuri SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi bwimbitse buratangaza uko ubwirinzi bw'umubiri buhangana na SARS-CoV-2 bwaba bumeze.
Ku bw'ibyo, dushobora gusa kwifashisha ubundi bushakashatsi ku zindi virusi za CoV, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Gab.4).
Muri rusange, nyuma yo gutera inyamaswa, virusi iramenyekana n'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri binyuze mu kwemeza inganda (PRR), zirimo C-type lectin-like receptor, Toll-like receptor (TLR), NOD-like receptor (NLR), na RIG-I-like receptor (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi ituma habaho kugaragaza ibintu by'ubushyuhe, gukura kw'insoro z'imiterere y'ingingo, no gukora interferon yo mu bwoko bwa I (IFN) igabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi no kwihutisha phagocytosis y'umwimerere wa virusi na macrophages.
Nyamara, poroteyine ya N yo muri SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha virusi kwirinda igisubizo cy'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri.
Nyuma y'igihe gito, ubwirinzi bw'umubiri buhindutse, bwatangiye kurwanya iyo virusi.
Uturemangingo two mu bwoko bwa T, turimo uturemangingo twa CD4+ na CD8+, ni two dufite uruhare rukomeye muri ubwo burinzi.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za CD4+ zituma ingirabuzimafatizo za B zikora abasirikare barwanya virusi, naho ingirabuzimafatizo za CD8+ zikamaraho burundu ingirabuzimafatizo za virusi.
Insoro T zitanga sitokinine zitera kubyimba kugira ngo zigire uruhare mu kurinda iyo ngirabuzimafatizo.
Icyakora, CoV ishobora gutuma udusimba twa T tutagira aho duhurira n'utundi duce duto tw'umubiri.
Ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, burimo ibigize umubiri, nka C3a na C5a, n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri nabyo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya ubwandu bwa virusi.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri babonetse mu barwayi bakize, bashoboye kurwanya MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo umubiri urenze urugero, ubwirinzi bw'umubiri butanga ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'ubwirinzi, zishobora kwangiza cyane imitsi y'ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu bihe bibi cyane, zikanagira ingaruka zikomeye ku ngingo ndetse no gupfa.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2, igaragazwa n'udutsiko tw'udutsiko tw'udutsiko, yibasira cyane cyane abantu bageze mu za bukuru bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero n'abagore batwite.
Muri rusange, abantu bagaragaweho virusi mu rugero rwagutse cyangwa bafite ubwirinzi butameze neza bafite amahirwe menshi yo kwandura kurusha abandi.
Ikigereranyo cy'igihe SARS-CoV-2 iba ikiri mu mubiri ni iminsi 1-14, cyane cyane iminsi 3-7 hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi ku barwayi 425 ba mbere bagaragaye muri Wuhan.
Nyamara, ubushakashatsi ku bantu 1.099 bagaragayeho ko igihe cyo kubaho k'ubwandu ari iminsi 3 kandi ko igihe cy'ubwandu kiba hagati y'iminsi 0 na 24.
Ubushakashatsi bushya bwavuzwe haruguru, bwagaragaje ko igihe cy'ubwiyongere ari iminsi 4,8 (3,0-7,2) hashingiwe ku mubare w'abantu 8,866.
Ni ngombwa ko inzego z'ubuzima zihindura igihe ntarengwa cyo kuguma mu kato hakurikijwe igihe cy'uburumbuke cy'indwara kugira ngo umuntu ufite ubwandu ariko utaragaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, atageza virusi ku bandi.
Nk'uko bisanzwe, abantu bagaragaweho virusi cyangwa bayanduye basabwa kujya mu kato k'iminsi 14.
Ese igihe cyo kubohora abantu cyagombye kongerwa kikagera ku minsi 24?
Ubushye ni ikimenyetso cy'ibanze n'icy'intangiriro cya COVID-19, buherekejwe cyangwa budaherekejwe n'ibindi bimenyetso birimo inkorora, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myanya y'umubiri, impyiko, kubabara umutwe, kubabara mu muhogo, kuruka mu mazuru, kubabara mu gatuza, kuribwa, impiswi, kugira isesemi, no kuruka.
Hari abarwayi bamwe na bamwe bagira ikibazo cy'umunaniro no/cyangwa indwara y'amaraso mu gihe cy'icyumweru kimwe nyuma yo kwandura.
Mu bihe bikomeye, indwara y'umurwayi ikomeza kwihuta igera mu ndwara y'ubuhumekero, indwara y'ubuhumekero, metabolic acidosis, na coagulopathy.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero n'umuriro ukabije, nubwo nta kibazo cyo gufata amashusho y'ibihaha, bagomba gupimwa virusi kugira ngo bashobore gusuzumwa hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwerekanye ko ibice by'ibimenyetso byari 98% by'ibicurane, 76% by'inkorora, 55% bya dyspnea, na 3% by'indwara y'ubuhumekero; 8% by'abarwayi bakeneye ubufasha bw'umwuka.
Ibyavuye muri ubwo bushakashatsi byatangajwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa, bwagaragajwe mu itsinda ry'imiryango no mu itsinda ry'abantu badahuje ubwoko.
Mu buryo buhabanye n'ubwo, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV bafite ibisa (98%), inkorora (47%) na dyspnea (55%) nk'ibimenyetso by'ibanze.
Nyamara, 80% by'abarwayi bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka, umubare uruta cyane uw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 kandi ugaragaza ko MERS ifite umubare munini w'abapfa kurusha COVID-19.
Indwara y'ubuhumekero (26%) n'umuhogo (21%) byabonetse no ku barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, umuriro (99%-100%), gukorora (29%-75%), guhumeka (40%-42%), diare (20-25%), no kubabara mu muhogo (13-25%) byerekanwa nk'ibimenyetso by'ibanze kandi ubufasha bwo guhumeka bukenewe ku kigero cya 14%-20% by'abarwayi.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abahitanywe na COVID-19 wari ku kigero cya 2% mu gihe abantu 66.576 ari bo bari bamaze kwandura ku isi.
Mu gihe mu kwezi kwa 11 mu 2002, SARS yari imaze guhitana abantu bagera ku 10% mu bantu 8.096 bari bayanduye.
Ku birebana na MERS, hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kwezi kwa Kamena 2012, umubare w'abapfuye ni 37% mu bantu 2.494 bemejwe ko banduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere bwagaragaje ko R0 ya SARS-CoV-2 igeze kuri 6.47 mu gihe intera yo kwizera (CI) ya 95% ari 5.71-7.23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV mu bimenyetso, igipimo cy'abapfuye n'igiteranyo cya R0 byatanzwe mu Gahunda ya 1.
Iyi mibare igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira cyane kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko nta bwo ari bwo bufite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira bw'indwara nka MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Ni yo mpamvu, ikibazo cyo kugenzura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiruta kure cyane icyorezo cya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Akenshi, abantu babaga batumiwe mu ngo cyangwa mu matsinda, cyangwa mu modoka, urugero nk'ubwato butwara abagenzi.
Akenshi, umurwayi aba afite amateka yo kuba yarigeze gutembera cyangwa kuba i Wuhan cyangwa ahandi hantu hazwi cyane cyangwa kuba yarahuye n'umuntu wanduye cyangwa umurwayi mu byumweru bibiri bishize mbere yo kwandura.
Ariko, bivugwa ko abantu bashobora gutwara virusi nta bimenyetso byayo mu gihe kirenze ibyumweru bibiri, kandi ko abamaze kuva mu bitaro bashobora kongera kuyitwara.
Mu gihe cy'intangiriro, umurwayi aba afite umubare w'insoro zera z'amaraso (cyane cyane lymphocytes) zisanzwe cyangwa zigabanutse.
Urugero, lymphopenia ifite umubare w'insoro zera z'amaraso < 4 × 109/L, ikubiyemo umubare w'utunyabuzima tw'insoro < 1 × 109/L, n'ubwinshi bwa aspartate aminotransferase ndetse na viremia byagaragaye mu barwayi 1,099 ba COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'indwara z'umwijima n'iz'ingingo ndetse na myoglobin byarazamutse mu maraso ya bamwe mu barwayi, ndetse na poroteyine C-reactive n'umuvuduko w'amaraso wo mu maraso byazamutse mu barwayi benshi.
Mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye, urugero rw'indwara ya D-dimer, ni ukuvuga ibintu bigabanya fibrine mu maraso, rurushaho kwiyongera, kandi umubare wa za lymphocyte uragenda ugabanuka.
Imyanya y'ibanga y'igifu iboneka mu barwayi benshi ba COVID-19 kandi ikagaragazwa n'ibisa n'ibicu bibiri cyangwa ubukana bw'ibirahuri mu bihaha.
Akenshi, abarwayi bagira umusonga udashyize, uburwayi bw'ibihaha bukomeye, n'indwara y'ubuhumekero (ARDS).
Iyo indwara ya ARDS igeze mu gihe runaka, ibishishwa byayo bitagira rutangira, amazi menshi yiyongera, kandi iyo ndwara igenda ikomera, ibyo bituma habaho ikibazo gikomeye cyo guhanahana umwuka.
Iyo umuntu afite Pneumocyte yo mu bwoko bwa I n'iyo mu bwoko bwa II, igipimo cy'ibinyabuzima by'ibumba kigabanuka, bityo umuvuduko w'ubuso ugakwira, bityo bikanagabanya ubushobozi bw'ibihaha bwo kwikuba, bityo bikongera ibyago byo guhorana impiswi y'ibihaha.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, ibisubizo bibi cyane mu ifoto ya thorax akenshi bijyana n'ikigero cy'indwara ikomeye.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryasuzumye ubwandu bw'impyiko z'amahaha, imiterere y'uruhu rwa hyaline, hamwe n'imikorere y'imyakura y'ibice byinshi by'uruhu mu bihaha by'abarwayi bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara, bikaba bihuye n'indwara y'ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera SIDA na ARDS ndetse no gusesengura kw'indwara z'abarwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Kugenzura RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rya RT-PCR, ni byo bikoreshwa cyane mu gusuzuma COVID-19.
Ariko, kubera igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ibinyoma, bishobora kwihutisha icyorezo, ibimenyetso by'indwara byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma (bitakibaye bishingiye gusa kuri RT-PCR) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu nk'ibyo byabayeho mu gusuzuma SARS.
Ni yo mpamvu, guhuza amateka y'indwara, ibimenyetso by'indwara, ibizamini byo muri laboratwari n'ibisubizo bya radiyoloji ari ingenzi kandi ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu ashobore gusuzuma neza.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2, bushobora gutahura ibice bya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 ikora mu buryo bw'imikorere ku 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kopi kuri microlitre imwe y'ibyinjira) ikoresheje inkoni y'imashini mu gihe cy'isaha imwe gusa kandi bidasabye ibikoresho bihambaye.
Twiringiye ko ubu buryo bushya buzatuma turushaho kumva neza kandi tukoroherwa mu gihe tuzaba tumaze kugenzura ko ari ukuri.
Kubera ko nta bumenyi buhagije bafite kuri CoVs nshya, abaganga batanga cyane cyane ubufasha mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19, mu gihe bagerageza imiti itandukanye yakoreshejwe cyangwa ivugwa mu kuvura izindi CoVs, nka SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo (Imbonerahamwe ya 2).2).
Ubu buryo bufite uburyo bwose bukoreshwa n'abaganga, harimo imiti igabanya ubukana, imiti igabanya ubukana bw'umubiri, imiti ya steroid, amaraso y'abantu bakize, imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa, n'ubufasha bw'imitekerereze.
Ndetse no muri za plasma z'abarwayi bakize, hari abateganyaga ko zakoreshwa mu buryo bwo kubavura.
Ibigo by'imiti byatangiye gukora imiti n'imiti yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Mu cyiciro cya mbere, SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha kandi ishobora no gutera ibindi bice byerekana ACE2 ku kigero cyo hasi, urugero nk'urwungano ngogozi n'impyiko.
Ariko kandi, indwara yo kubura umwuka no kudahumeka ni byo bibangamiye abarwayi kandi ni byo bihitana benshi.
Ni yo mpamvu ubufasha bwo guhumeka ari ingenzi mu koroshya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima, harimo ubufasha bw'umwuka wa oxygene, umwuka wo hejuru, guhumeka bidakomeye, no guhumeka mu buryo bukomeye, bitewe n'uburwayi.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bagomba gufashwa na oxygenation ya membrane extracorporeal (ECMO), ni uburyo buhindutse bwo kuvura umutima bukoreshwa mu kuvura umutima utera cyangwa guhumeka bibangamiye ubuzima.
Byongeye kandi, kwita ku mizi ya electrolyte, kwirinda no kuvura indwara z'ibyorezo na shock ya septic, no kurinda imikorere y'ibice by'ingenzi by'umubiri ni ingenzi cyane ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Imikorere mibi y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri izwiho gutera cystokin cyorezo mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Igitero cya cytokine ni uburyo bwo gusubiza indwara ziterwa n'ubushye bwaranzwe no gushyiraho uruvange rw'izindi cytokine, zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Iyi myokarite ituma abarwayi bagahita bakira vuba, bityo bakaba bashobora no kwiyahura.
Immunosuppression ni ingenzi cyane mu kuvura cytocyte cy cyclonic, cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite ikibazo gikomeye.
Kortikosteroide na Tocilizumab, umurwayi w'umubiri wa monoclonal anti-IL6, byakoreshejwe mu kuvura ibihuha bya cytokine.
Ubundi buryo bwo kurwanya ubudahangarwa bwa sitokine bw'inkubi y'umuvuduko w'umubiri harimo uburyo bwo kurwanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri buyobowe na za sel T; gukumira IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; gukumira JAK; blinatumomab; gukumira ibimenyetso bya sitokine 4; na inhibitor ya HDAC.
Steroide, nk'immunosuppresse, zikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura SARS mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara.
Ariko, imiti ya steroid ku gipimo cyo hejuru ntabwo igira akamaro ku barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bw'ibihaha bukomeye.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, za steroid zishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye, cyane cyane uburwayi bw'amagufwa, bugira ingaruka cyane ku myanzuro.
Nyamara, gutanga kortikosteroide mu gihe gito mu bipimo bito cyangwa bito, byasabwe ko byitonderwa ku barwayi barwaye cyane ba COVID-19.
Kugeza ubu, nta muti wa virusi wemejwe ko ugira ingaruka ku muntu.
Ariko, gutanga remdesivir mu buryo bw'amaraso, ikinyuranyo cya nucleotide, byaragaragaye ko bifite akamaro ku murwayi w'Umunyamerika wa COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya uvura indwara zitandukanye wakorewe na Gilead, wakoreshwaga mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi za Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma, remdesivir yagaragaje ubudahangarwa ku yindi virusi ya RNA y'imiterere imwe, harimo MERS na SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uru rukingo kugira ngo rukore isuzuma ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo by'izo ngamba byari bitegerejwe cyane.
