Kubera ko iyi virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 na SARS na byo bikaba bisa, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyasaga n'icy'icyorezo cya SARS.
Ariko, hari itandukaniro ry'ingenzi hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, rikenewe cyane mu gukumira icyorezo no mu kwita ku barwayi.
COVID-19 yibasiye cyane abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, yibasiye cyane abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi umubare w'abapfa uraruta uw'abageze mu za bukuru.
Umubare w'abapfuye bishwe na SARS wari hejuru y'uwishwe na COVID-19 (10.91% ugereranyije na 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakunze kwanduza virusi n'ubwo baba batagaragaza ibimenyetso, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bakunze kwanduza virusi mu gihe barwaye cyane. Ibi bituma bigorana cyane mu guhashya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 ugereranyije na SARS.
Ibi bisobanuye mu buryo bumwe impamvu SARS-CoV-2 yandura vuba kandi ikagenda cyane kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibizamini bisanzwe bya RNA byo gusuzuma SARS-CoV-2 bishobora gutanga umusaruro mubi ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, umurwayi wakize ashobora kongera kugaragaza ko afite virusi.
Ibyo bintu byaje kongera ibyago byo gukwirakwira kw'iyo virusi.
Nubwo ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 bugenda buza vuba, hari ibibazo by'ingenzi bikiri mu nzira:
Ese SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 ifite ihuriro ku kigero cya 96% hagati yayo na CoV ebyiri zimeze nka SARS zo mu bwoko bw'igicuri, ntidushobora kwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse mu gitsina cy'igicuri.
Ni ibihe biremwa by'ingenzi by'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa byanduza virusi ziva ku nyamaswa zo mu muryango, urugero nk'urukwavu, zikaza ku bantu?
Niba tutaramenya ibisubizo bya mbere na kabiri, ntitwaba twabigize umwuga, kandi icyorezo gishobora kongera kwaduka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo ibipimo byo mu rwego rwa molekeri n'ibya shimi byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na ACE2, ni gute koko virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzima y'ubuhumekero igatuma habaho impinduka z'indwara?
Ese iyi virusi yaba ifitanye isano n'ingirabuzimafatizo zigaragaza ACE2 mu zindi ngingo?
Mu gihe tutabonye ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kwihutira kubona indwara cyangwa kuyivura neza.
Ese iyi cyorezo kizahoraho igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ikura mu buryo bw'imiterere mu gihe cy'ubwandu hagati y'abantu?
Ese iyi ndwara izagera ku isi hose, ihere nk'indwara ya SARS, cyangwa izongera igaragaze mu bihe nk'ibi nk'ibi by'ibicurane?
Ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo hamwe n'ibindi byinshi, ni iby'ingenzi cyane, ariko bishobora gufata igihe kirekire kugira ngo tubishakishe.
Nyamara, nubwo byaba byatugora, nta bundi buryo dufite uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba na bwangu kugira ngo dushobore gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Inkomoko ya virusi ya corona mu bantu
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, ihinduka n'imiterere y'umubiri byagiye bituma koronavirusi (CoV) n'izindi mikorobe zayo, harimo n'abantu, zihangana.
Mbere ya 2003, koronavirusi ebyiri z'abantu (HCoV) zari zizwiho gutera indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS n'icy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byahinduye ibintu, bigaragaza ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kwangiza no guhitana abantu.
Kuzamuka kwa SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 kwatumye CoV igaruka ku isura igatangaza abantu cyane bitewe n'uko ishobora kwandura cyane, ariko ikaba ifite ubushobozi buke bwo kwanduza kurusha SARS-CoV.
Kubera ko HCoVs zanduye ari zoonotic, kumenya inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bizadufasha.
HCoVs nyinshi zikomoka ku ducurama. Muri izo nyamaswa, virusi ntabwo ifite ubukana.
Abashakashatsi benshi bagaragaje ko HCoVs za mbere zabonetse mu bwoko bwa HCoVs, ariko ko zabonetse mu bwoko bwa HCoVs bwa mbere.
Kumenya imiterere y'inyamaswa bifite ingaruka ku kurinda indwara z'abantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire ya CoV-inang mu nyamaswa na bwo bushobora gutanga ubushishozi bw'ingenzi ku miterere ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga isesengura ry'ubumenyi dufite kuri HCoVs ndwi, twibanda ku mateka y'ihuriro ryazo ndetse n'inkomoko yazo zo mu nyamaswa ndetse no kwanduzanya hagati y'ubwoko bwazo.
Icy'ingenzi, twahurije hamwe izo virusi dufatiye ku miterere yazo n'uburyo zikorana.
Icyorezo cya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) kirimo kuvugwa muri iyi context.
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa kugira ngo haboneke ihinduka ry'imikorere y'abashakanye n'ingaruka z'ubwoko bw'indwara virusi ifite ku buremere bw'indwara.
Koronavirusi (CoV) ni mwene Coronaviridae, igizwe n'itsinda rya virusi za RNA z'uruhu rw'umwimerere, z'uruhu rumwe.
Iyi virusi ifite genom nini cyane ifite ubunini bwa kilobase 26 kugeza kuri 32 mu zindi virusi za RNA zitwa "CoV", kubera imiterere yayo isa n'ikamba ry'umwami munsi ya microscope ya electron.
Dukurikije imiterere yayo, CoV ifite genomes zitarasobanuwe zifite gahunda isa.
Hafi 2/3 by'imiterere y'umubiri w'umuntu, igizwe n'uduce twinshi tw'inyuguti (ORF1a na ORF1b) tubyirukaho, twose dusobanurwa na pp1a na pp1ab.
Iyi polyprotein ikomeza gukorerwa indi mirimo itandukanye kugira ngo ibone poroteyine 16 zidakurikije imiterere, yitwa nsp1~16.
Ibisigaye by'iyo genome bigizwe n'ibisate by'ibanze (ORF) by'amaraso bigizwe na poroteyine z'imiterere, harimo ibihu (S), udusobekerane (E), membrane (M), na nucleoproteine (N).
Hariho kandi poroteyine z'inyongera z'ubwoko runaka zandikwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Kubera gutandukana kw'imiterere ya poroteyine, CoVs zigirwa mu moko ane (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, na delta-CoV); muri ayo moko ane, genus ya beta-CoV ni yo ifite umubare munini wa za HCoVs kandi igabanya mu matsinda ane (A, B, C, na D).
Ibimenyetso bya phylogenetic byerekana ko ibisebe n'imbeba ari byo bihingwa by'ibinyabuzima byinjiza za virusi bya alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zifite ibigega by'ubwoko bwa gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi, CoVs yagiye ikomeza kwambuka umupaka w'ubwoko, ndetse zimwe muri zo zahindutse udukoko dutera indwara ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kuvumburwa CoVs zirindwi z'abantu (HCoVs).
Muri izo virusi uko ari zirindwi, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni za alfa-CoV.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, koronavirusi y'ubuhumekero ikaze cyane (SARS-CoV), koronavirusi y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV), na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, na HCoV-NL63 byanze bikunze byatera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'inyonko na/cyangwa isuka.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zifite ubushobozi bukomeye bwo gukwirakwiza indwara, zikaba zitera ubwandu bw'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero bworoheje ku barwayi benshi kandi zikaba zifite amahirwe menshi yo gutera indwara z'ubuhumekero bukabije (ARDS) no kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara mu bice by'ubuhumekero.
HCoV-229E ya mbere, B814, yavanywe mu mwuka w'umuntu ufite ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwarashyizwe mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse ku byerekeye HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bikaba byaratumye ibimenyetso byayo byiyongera.
Mu by'ukuri, kugeza igihe habonekeye icyorezo cya SARS, abantu benshi bemeraga ko ubwandu bwa HCoV nta cyo butwaye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu mwaka wa 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo by'indwara byahitanye abantu benshi mu mateka, cyahitanye abantu barenga 8.000 n'umubare w'abapfuye ungana na 10%.
Hashize imyaka icumi, icyorezo cya MERS cyatangiye gukwirakwira mu gice cy'Abarabu, gikomeza kwiyongeraho n'ibindi bice by'isi.
HCoV nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV), ikomeza kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo ntandaro y'icyorezo cy'indwara ya koronavirusi ya 2019 (COVID-19), yahitanye abantu barenga 3.120 kandi yanduza abantu barenga 91.000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Abantu bamaze kumva ko ibintu byihutirwa kandi ko isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Izo virusi zirindwi zose zikomoka ku nyamaswa, ni ukuvuga ko zikomoka ku mibonano mpuzabitsina, ku ngurube, ku mbeba cyangwa ku nyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi byemeza ko HCoV zose zaturutse mu nguge. Mu nguge, CoV irahuza neza kandi ntiyitera indwara, ariko igaragaza itandukaniro rikomeye rya jenoside.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, siyansi, imibereho n'amahame mbwirizamuco mu Bushinwa no ku isi yose.
Gushakisha inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bitanga ishingiro ryo gusobanukirwa amateka y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, imbaraga zituma habaho, n'uburyo ibyo bimenyetso bibuza ubwoko runaka kwimuka.
Ubu bushakashatsi bushobora kandi kuyobora cyangwa korohereza gushakisha inyamaswa zo mu bwihisho, abahuza, no kongera ingano za SARS-CoV-2, bikaba bifite akamaro kanini mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nkuru, twabasobanuriye inkomoko ya zoonotic, uburyo bwo kwanduzanya hagati y'ubwoko butandukanye, n'uburyo HCoVs zanduza.
Twagaragaje by'umwihariko kandi tuganira ku ngingo rusange y'uko virusi y'umurwayi wa HCoV ubusanzwe iba itari indwara mu mazi yayo, ariko ikaba indwara nyuma yo kuyikwirakwiza mu zindi nyamaswa.
Twagaragaje kandi ko mu iterambere rya HCoV, kwiyongera kw'ubushobozi bwo kuyandura akenshi bijyana no kugabanuka kw'indwara.
Ibyavuye mu cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 na byo byashyizwe muri iyo nama.
CoV zo mu nyamaswa zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1930.
Mbere y'uko ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwo mu bwoko bwa B814 bw'abantu barwaye ibicurane butorwa mu mubiri w'umuntu, za CoV zitandukanye zari zarabonetse mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, amakoya n'imbwa.
Mu myaka icumi ishize, hamaze kuvumburwa virusi za HCoV zirindwi.
Igisobanuro kigufi ku mateka y'ibanze yo kuvumburwa kwa HCoV mu buryo bw'igihe (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) ni igishushanyo mbonera cy'amakuru.
HCoV-229E ya mbere yatoranyijwe mu musarane w'umuntu ufite ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero bwo hejuru mu 1966, nyuma yaje guhindurwa kugira ngo ikure mu cyuma cy'ubwoko bwa WI-38.
Abantu banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaza ibimenyetso bya serumu, birimo kurwara umutwe, gusohora, kugira umunaniro, no kubabara mu muhogo, bikagendana n'umuriro n'inkorora bigaragara ku kigero kiri hagati ya 10 na 20% by'abanduye.
Mu mwaka wa 1967, HCoV-OC43 yaje kwanduzwa n'ibinyabuzima by'umubiri no gukwirakwizwa mu bwonko bw'igicuri cy'igicuri cy'ubwana bw'ibere.
Amagenwa y'indwara ya HCoV-OC43 asa n'aho ari nk'indwara iterwa na HCoV-229E, kandi ntiyagaragazwa mu buryo bw'ibimenyetso ko ari yo ituma umuntu yanduzwa n'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nka virusi ya influenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 zikwirakwira ku isi hose kandi zikunze gukwirakwizwa cyane mu gihe cy'imbeho mu duce dufite ikirere cyiza.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo kubyara kiri munsi y'icyumweru kimwe, gikurikirwa n'igihe cy'uburwayi cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu b'abakorerabushake, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E bagize ibicurane byoroheje.
Ni bake cyane mu barwayi bafite ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri bw'umubiri wa muntu bukomeye, bagaragaza uburwayi bw'ubuhumekero bwo hasi.
SARS, nanone izwi ku izina rya "pneumonia atypical", ni cyo cyorezo cya mbere cya HCoV cyagaragaye mu mateka y'abantu, kandi SARS-CoV ni yo yabaye intandaro yacyo, ni na yo ya gatatu yagaragaye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabonetse bwa mbere mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateye abantu 8,096 banduye n'abantu 774 bapfuye, mu bihugu byinshi no mu migabane.
Uretse kuba umuntu ari super-virusi, buri murwayi wese ashobora kuba afite abantu babiri bamwanduye, mu gihe cyo kurama kikaba kiri hagati y'iminsi 4 na 7 kandi virusi ikaze cyane iba ku munsi wa 10 w'indwara.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV babanza kugira indwara ya myalgia, kubabara umutwe, kugira umuriro, kugira umunaniro no kugira igogora, bikurikirwa no kugira impumuro nke, inkorora no guhumeka nabi nk'ibimenyetso by'inyongera.
Lymphopenia, ibipimo by'imikorere y'umwijima bidasanzwe, n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushake bw'umubiri (creatine kinase) ni bimwe mu bibazo by'ibizamini byo muri laboratwari bikunze kugaragara muri SARS.
Kugabanuka kw'imikorere y'udutsi two mu nda, kw'umusemburo w'uruhu, no kongera kw'imikorere y'udutsi two mu nda nabyo byarabonetse mu barwayi ba SARS.
Ikindi kandi, abagera kuri 20-30% by'abarwayi baba bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka.
Uretse mu buhumekero bwo hasi, hari inzego zimwe na zimwe zirimo urwungano ngogo, impyiko, n'impyiko nazo zishobora kwandura mu gihe gikomeye, akenshi bijyana n'inkubi ya cytokine, ishobora kwica, cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite ubudahangarwa buke.
Virusi ya mbere yatoranyijwe mu isuzuma ry'ibihaha ry'umwe mu bavandimwe b'umurwayi wa mbere w'ibanze wari wavuye i Guangzhou akajya i Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, ingufu nyinshi zashyizwe mu bushakashatsi ku mikorobe za HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yavumbuwe mu mwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Iyi virusi yabanje kugaragara cyane mu bana bato, mu basaza, no mu barwayi bafite ubwirinzi buke bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Imyambarire ya korizo, conjunctivitis, umuriro, na bronchiolitis ni byo bikunze kugaragara ku ndwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga bwasobanuye iby'ubwoko bw'agakoko gatera indwara y'umwijima bw'umwana w'amezi 8 ufite impyiko muri Holande.
Nubwo iyo virusi yagaragaye mu Buholandi, mu by'ukuri yakwirakwijwe ku isi hose.
HCoV-NL63 igereranywa ko ifite uruhare rwa 4.7% mu ndwara rusange z'ubuhumekero kandi iboneka cyane mu mpeshyi, mu gihe cy'impeshyi no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano na laryngite y'ubuhumekero, nanone bita croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yavanywe mu mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari wararembeye mu bitaro arwaye pneumoniya na bronchiolitis muri Hong Kong.
Usibye pneumonia na bronchiolitis zo mu baturage, HCoV-HKU1 bivugwa ko ifitanye isano no kongera icyorezo cy'ubuhumekero.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 iboneka ku isi hose, kandi itera indwara zo mu buhumekero buciriritse.
Iyi miryango ine ya HCoV yose yarahindutse ku bantu kandi muri rusange bafite ibyago bike byo guhinduka indwara ikomeye. Nubwo bimeze bityo, hari igihe bidasanzwe bibayeho kubera impamvu zitazwi, nk'uko bimeze ku bwoko bwa HCoV-NL63 bw'ubwoko bwa virusi bwa vuba aha bwavuzwe ko bwateje uburwayi bukomeye bw'ubuhumekero mu Bushinwa.
Muri rusange, iyo HCoVs zifite ubushobozi bwo kwimuka neza no gukomeza kwicungira mu bantu, ubukana n'ubwandu bwazo na byo biragabanuka.
MERS-CoV yatangiranye mu mwaka wa 2012 mu bihaha by'umuntu ufite imyaka 60 y'amavuko ufite pneumonia ikaze n'uburwayi bw'impyiko muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Nubwo abenshi mu banduye bagaragaye muri laboratwari bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati, hari abanduye b'abanyamahanga bagiye baturuka mu bindi bihugu byo mu Burayi no muri Tuniziya.
Indi ndwara y'icyorezo yibasiye Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 aho abantu 186 bayanduye.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS bisa n'ibimenyetso bya SARS, birangwa no kwiyongera kw'ibicurane by'umwimerere.
Bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi ba MERS nabo barwaye impyiko zifite ikibazo, kugeza ubu MERS ni yo yonyine ihura na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byo mu nda no mu nda, nko kugira isesemi no kwihekura.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abarwayi 2500 byemejwe na laboratwari, n'umubare munini w'abapfa, ni ukuvuga 34,4%, byatumye MERS-CoV iba imwe muri za virusi ziteye ubwoba cyane zizwi ku bantu.
Mu kwezi kwa 12 hagati kugeza mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, havumbuwe ikigo cy'abarwayi ba pneumonia bagaragaye ko bafite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero bw'ubuhumekero bw'amajyaruguru ziterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zihuta ku isi (Global Health Emergency) cyise COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, abamaze kwandura ku isi bose bari 90,053, naho abamaze guhitanwa n'icyorezo bari ku kigero cya 3,4%.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko umubare w'abanduye muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa, wari 4.2%, naho mu bindi bihugu wari 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 ituma umuntu ahumeka indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zirimo umuriro, inkorora n'ubuhumekero.
Indwara y'impiswi nayo yabonetse mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe.
Impumoni ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye cyane kandi bishobora guhita bihinduka indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zisa cyane bitewe n'ubumwe bwazo bwo hejuru bw'umurongo wa nucleotide, ku kigero cya 82%, zombi zishyira hamwe mu mashami atandukanye y'igiti cya phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwiza indwara buciriritse, ariko ishobora kwanduza kurusha SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 ariko nta bimenyetso bagaragaje, byanavuzwe ko bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira ku isi mu buryo bwihuse.
Kugereranya no gutandukanya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi HCoV esheshatu byerekana ibintu bishishikaje cyane bifitanye isano ndetse n'ibyo itandukaniyeho.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo gutwita n'igihe indwara ya HCoV imara birasa cyane.
Muri ubwo buryo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza icyiciro rusange cy'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buri hagati ya SARS-CoV na HCoV enye z'imiryango (n'ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza isura rusange igaragara ku bwandu bwa HCoVs zo mu bwoko bwa Community, harimo isura y'ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, umubare muto w'abantu barwaye COVID-19 ikomeye ushobora kugaragara nk'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV nubwo ari bake ugereranyije.
Icya gatatu, SARS-CoV-2 nayo yagaragaje ibimenyetso bishishikaje, bifite aho bihuriye n'iby'izindi HCoV zo mu baturage ndetse na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukwirakwiza virusi nyinshi cyane nk'uko HCoVs zo mu bwoko bw'abantu zikwirakwiza.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaranduye cyane nyuma y'uko hari inzira zimwe na zimwe mu bantu zari zikiriho ariko zikaba zitagomba kugenzurwa, nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Ubundi, kimwe n'izindi HCoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragazwa n'ibipimo by'imyanda.
"Niba se SARS-CoV-2 yanduye mu kanwa no mu itako yagize uruhare runini, nk'uko byagenze ku mwikubo wa SARS-CoV, nibura mu bihe bimwe na bimwe, bizasobanurwa n'ubushakashatsi buzakurikiraho".
Ikindi cy'ingenzi ni ukumenya niba SARS-CoV-2 igenda ihindagurika nk'uko byagenze ku HCoVs zo mu bwoko bw'abantu.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, uko SARS-CoV-2 izaba imeze, hakubiyemo uburyo ishobora kwandura, ubukana bwayo n'uburyo ishobora gukwirakwira mu bantu, bizagira ingaruka zikomeye ku iherezo ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje.
Izo koronavirusi enye z'ubwoko bwa HCoV z'abantu zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, zose zimaze kumenyera abantu.
Ku rundi ruhande, umuntu yavuga ko abantu bamaze kumenyera HCoVs enye.
Mu yandi magambo, HCoV n'abantu bashobora kuba ari ubwoko bw'abantu ba mbere barokotse icyorezo cya HCoV.
