Zimwe muri zo zoonotic CoVs zigaragara mu mashyamba.
By'umwihariko, CoVs zo mu ducurama zishobora kuba zo zoonotic ziratandukanye cyane.
Hari amahirwe menshi ko iyi virusi zo zo zoonotic ishobora guhinduka ikongera ikabyara izindi virusi, bigatuma haboneka indi virusi ishobora kwandura mu buryo bworoshye kandi ishobora no kwica abantu mu gihe kiri imbere.
