Ibisubizo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'indwara ibibazwa n'ibiba byemejwe bya COVID-19 bigomba kuvugururwa
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryashyize ahagaragara inama yihuse ku bijyanye no gusuzuma no kuvura ubwandu bushya bwa koronavirusi ya 2019 (2019-nCoV). Iyo nama ishingiye ku byo twabonye kandi ni inama nziza yo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi.
Nubwo bimeze bityo, icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu buragenda bwiyongera bushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; kubera iyo mpamvu, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura buragenda buhinduka.
Muri iyi baruwa, twasubije ku gitekerezo kimwe mu byatangajwe mu mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibiranga indwara biheruka gusuzumwa ku "bakekwaho" n'"abemejwe" hashingiwe ku Mabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (verisiyo ya karindwi) yashyizweho na Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'abaturage ba Repubulika y'u Bushinwa.
Mu Kuboza 2019, koronavirusi nshya yo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo, ubu cyiswe mu buryo bw'amategeko indwara ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) kandi virusi yiswe coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikomeye cyane 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yagaragaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Kugira ngo turwanye ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryakoze igitabo cy'inama zihuse kandi cyasohotse ku rubuga rwa Military Medical Research ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020.
Ubuyobozi bw'iryo tsinda bwatumye abantu benshi barishyiraho.
Icyakora, ni ngombwa kumenya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, kandi ko ubumenyi dufite kuri yo bugenda bwiyongera dukurikije ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; ni yo mpamvu uburyo bwo kuyisuzuma no kuyivura bugenda buhinduka.
Urugero, Igitabo cy'Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza 3 Werurwe 2020, iyi komisiyo yasohoye inyandiko zirindwi zose, zimwe murizo zarahinduwe cyane.
Ubuyobozi bwacu bwemeye ibitekerezo bya Zhou et al. bashyizeho uburyo bworoshye bwo gutanga amanota hashingiwe kubyo babonye mu buvuzi.
Ibisubizo by'akazi kabo byongereye ubuhamya bushya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi bihindura ubuhamya bw'ingenzi ku byerekeye iki cyorezo ku isi.
Twashyigikiye umurimo wabo w'ingenzi kandi turabibashimira.
Ariko kandi, ibyo bagezeho mu bushakashatsi bwabo bikeneye kuvugururwa hashingiwe ku buyobozi bushya bw'ubuvuzi bw'indwara ya COVID-19 (ubushakashatsi bwa karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi bushya.
Dukurikije icyanditswe cya karindwi (ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo hamenyekane umuntu ukekwaho kwandura indwara, hakenewe guhuza inkuru imwe y'icyorezo n'ibintu bibiri by'ubuvuzi kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura ryimbitse, cyangwa hakenewe ibintu bitatu by'ubuvuzi mu gihe nta mateka y'ubuvuzi asobanutse neza:
Amateka ya Epidemiyoloji: (1) amateka yo gutembera cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 babonetse mu minsi 14 mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso; (2) amateka yo kuba warigeze guhura n'umuntu wanduye SARS-CoV-2 (wipimishije aside ya nucleic acid yageze ku gisubizo cyiza); (3) amateka yo guhura n'umurwayi ufite ibicurane cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 babonetse mu minsi 14 mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso; (4) amateka yo guhura n'abantu bafite ibicurane byemejwe (abantu 2 cyangwa barenga bafite ibicurane cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 2 mu duce duto, nko mu ngo, mu biro, mu ishuri, n'ahandi).
Ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero; (2) ibimenyetso byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'amaraso y'umweru agaragaza umubare usanzwe, ugabanuka cyangwa ugabanuka mu maraso y'ubwoko bwa lymphocyte mu gihe cy'indwara ya mbere.
Gusuzuma indwara yemewe bigomba gushingira ku muntu ukekwaho indwara ufite ibimenyetso bya virusi cyangwa virusi bikurikira: (1) isuzuma rya PCR ryihariye ryakozwe mu gihe nyacyo ryagaragaje ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite virusi; (2) urutonde rwose rw'imiterere y'agakoko gatera virusi rugaragaza ko virusi nshya ya koronavirusi ifite virusi nyinshi; (3) ibizamini bya seriumu byerekana ko hari udukoko dutandukanye two mu bwoko bwa IgM n'utwo mu bwoko bwa IgG two mu bwoko bwa IgG two mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2; cyangwa se, guhindura udukoko dutandukanye two mu bwoko bwa IgG two mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 two mu bwoko bwa IgG two mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 tukava ku gitsina, cyangwa se tukagaragaza ko twagize virusi mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi bw'indwara, cyangwa se ko twagize ubwandu burenze inshuro 4 mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi.
Dushobora kubona ko ibizamini bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo bya aside ya nucleic mu bipimo by'umuyoboro w'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso byongewe ku nshuro ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'iya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Ibimenyetso bya pathogenic by'ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe mu cyiciro cya kane (tariki ya 27 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatanu (tariki ya 8 Gashyantare 2020); noneho, ibimenyetso bya seroloji byongerewe mu cyiciro cya karindwi.
Iyi mpinduka ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi mu gushaka ibikoresho byiza byo gutahura aside ya nikeleyeri mu buryo bwihuse, ndetse n'ibipimo by'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero harimo no gufata amaraso, byongera umubare w'ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi bigashyigikira ko ibipimo by'umubiri runaka byemezwa.
Ikindi kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigenda byiyongera bidusaba kuba maso ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara y'umutima ndetse n'abadafite ibimenyetso byayo.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, imbonerahamwe y'imiterere ya Zhou et al. igomba kuvugururwa kuko bashyira abantu badafite ibimenyetso byihariye nk'abafite ibyago bike.
Urwo rwego kandi rugomba kugenzurwa mu bikorwa no mu bushakashatsi bw'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko hari ibimenyetso by'ibanze bizagaragara, tugasaba abasomyi bacu kugira icyo babivugaho.
Ku bijyanye no gusuzuma "abakekwaho iyi ndwara" n'"abemejwe ko bayanduye", turabasaba gukurikiza no kubahiriza amabwiriza mashya mu bihugu byabo.
Itsinda ryacu rizongera rijye rihindura amabwiriza yacu buri gihe kugira ngo bidufashe.
Bangladesh yongeye guhitana abantu batanu bishwe na COVID-19 ku munsi wa mbere
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje ko abantu batanu bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Iyi ni yo mibare y'abantu benshi bapfuye ku munsi umwe bazize iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo cy'Ubushakashatsi ku ndwara z'ibyorezo, no kugenzura no gukumira indwara (IEDCR) cyo muri Bangladesh cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye wari 114, naho 33 bari barakize bakaba bari mu rugo.
Abantu 17 bahasize ubuzima.
