Umukozi w'ibitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikigo cy'amakuru cyo muri ako gace, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo yo kurwanya ruswa yo muri Bengali, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Kuwa gatandatu, mu itangazo ry'amashusho ryatangajwe kuri interineti, Minisitiri w'Ingabo n'Ubutwererane, Obaidul Quader, yavuze ko ingendo rusange zizakomeza guhagarara kugeza kuwa gatandatu.
Iri gabanywa ry'ingendo muri rusange ryatangiye ku ya 26 Werurwe, rikaba ryateganyijwe kurangira ku wa gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Gutwara ibintu by'ibanze nk'imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa biracyemewe.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 muri Bangladesh yagaragaye ku ya 8 Werurwe, ku bantu babiri bari bavuye mu Butaliyani ndetse n'umugore wa umwe muri bo.
