SARS-CoV-2 imaze kwandura abantu barenga miliyoni ku isi
Ku wa kane, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus ya SARS-CoV-2 warenze miliyoni imwe ku isi, nk'uko byatangajwe na Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Abantu bagera ku bihumbi 52 bamaze guhitanwa na COVID-19, indwara iterwa na koronavirusi.
Iki gikorwa cyabaye ku munsi umwe n'uwo Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwayo bwa mbere bwa koronavirusi na Zambiya ifite umuntu wa mbere yahitanye.
Ku wa kane, Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ko ari kimwe mu bihugu bike bikiri mu gihugu kitarimo icyorezo cya koronavirusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko habonetse abantu 1.051.635, barimo 79.332 mu masaha makumyabiri n'ane kuva saa kumi za mu gitondo ku isaha yo mu Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC) ku ya 4 Mata.
