Ubucuruzi bwo muri Ositaraliya bwagabanyije umubare w'utuntu twabugenewe kugura buri mugabane
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nyuma ya saa sita, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya ya Woolworth na Coles yagabanyije umubare w'amapaki y'ubwiherero ku isoko rimwe, ku maduka yose ku rwego rw'igihugu.
ALDI nayo yashyizeho itegeko ryo gutwara umufuka umwe ku wa mbere.
Ibi byatangajwe nk'ubutumwa ku biro by'itora no ku rukuta rwe rwa Facebook.
Abaguzi batangiye kubika ibikoresho kubera ubwoba bw'uko COVID-19 ishobora gutuma abaturage batangira kwigunga.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije igiciro cy'impapuro z'isuku zo kohereza mu ngo ku gipfunyika kimwe ku busa.
Iyi mpinduka ikurikiyeho amabwiriza yo gufunga ibicuruzwa mu masoko ane, yari yashyizweho na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
Mu itangazo rye ryo ku ya 8 Werurwe, Coles yatangaje ko mu gushyiraho imipaka y'amapaki ane, "amaduka menshi yari agifite ibicuruzwa byose mu isaha imwe gusa kuva byoherejwe", kandi avuga ko ibyo bisabwa "bitigeze bibaho", mu gihe ALDI, mu nyandiko yo kuri Facebook ku wa kabiri, yavuze ko "bitari byitezwe".
Umuvugizi wa Woolworths yavuze ko mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa byazamutse cyane.
Costco yo muri Canberra na yo yagabanyije umubare w'ibyo yahagaze kugeza ku bipfunyika bibiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo Coles yirinde kubura, yategetse ibicuruzwa binini mubikoresho byatanzwe kandi yongera inshuro zoherezwa, Woolworths yategetse ibikoresho byiyongereye, mugihe ALDI ikoze ibikoresho byo kwimenyekanisha ibikorwa byahariwe kuwa gatatu.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishyirahamwe ry'abakora ubucuruzi muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ububiko, ariko ko inzego za leta z'ibanze mu gihe cyo kohereza amakamyo byamugoraga.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa bizamuka, mu gihe abatanga ibicuruzwa bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi ko hazabaho imihigo mike yo kwamamaza.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko kubera ko yari yambuye ibicuruzwa mbere, amaduka amwe n'amwe ntiyashoboye kugira umwihariko ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru y'ikinyamakuru News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, inzobere mu by'ubucuruzi muri kaminuza ya Queensland y'ikoranabuhanga, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibyo yagenewe buri mugoroba.
Yashimangiye ko amatembabuzi y'ubwiherero ari ikintu gifite ubunini bwinshi ku buryo umubare w'ibikoresho bihari uba ari muto kandi iyo bigurishijwe, bituma haboneka umwanya munini w'ubusa ku mashyiga ku buryo ubukene bw'ibintu burushaho kwiyongera.
Coles na Woolworths bavuga ko [ko] niba hari ibintu byinshi ku mashuka, niba ibicuruzwa nk'utugambo two mu bwiherero n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rw'ubuziranenge bishobora [kugurwa] kandi bikaba bihari mu bwinshi, ubwoba bushobora kugabanyuka, nk'uko Russel Zimmerman abivuga abinyujije kuri ABC News.
Uruganda rukora impapuro z'isuku z'isuku z'isuku zongeye gukoreshwa ruvuga ko kuwa gatatu w'icyumweru gishize rwabuze ibyo rukoresha.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora impapuro z'isuku za Kleenex, na Solaris Paper, ikora Sorbent, byashimangiye ko bakorana amasaha 24 kuri 24 mu rwego rwo gukomeza gutanga ibikoresho, nk'uko bitangazwa na News.com.au.
Ikinyamakuru Domain.com, cyandika ku mbuga z'imyuga, cyatangaje ko abacuruzi bamwe na bamwe batanga impapuro z'isuku ku bantu babanza gutanga amaramuko mu cyamunara cya Melbourne, mu gihe abaguzi bari kugabanuka kubera ko abaguzi bari mu kiruhuko cy'iminsi y'akazi.
Ikinyamakuru NT News cyo ku wa kane, cyandikirwa i Darwin, cyanditse impapuro umunani z'inyandiko zari zigenewe gukatwa no gukoreshwa nk'agakarita k'isuku.
Ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa by'ibinyamwuga ntibashakaga gushyiraho amategeko, nk'uko byatangajwe na ABC Australia ku ya 3 Werurwe, bavuga ko batateganyaga gushyiraho amategeko agenga ibyo kugura.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko ibindi bicuruzwa na byo biri mu bicuruzwa cyane, birimo udupfukamunwa, imiti igabanya imyanda, ibiryo byumye, isabune yo gukaraba intoki, n'ifu.
No hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku cyumweru nyuma ya saa sita, supermarket yo mu Bwongereza Ocado yagaragaje ko igomba kugabanya igiciro cy'amapositi y'isuku ya Andres kugeza ku macupa abiri arimo imiferege 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) ryemeje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye cyatewe na koronavirusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryumvikanisha gusa ubukana bw'icyorezo, aho kugaragaza ubukana bw'indwara, OMS ivuga ko ari ngombwa gukangurira leta kugira icyo ikora:
Ibihugu byose birashobora guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Iyo ibihugu byibonye, bikora ibizamini, bikorohereza, bikirinda, bikongera abaturage mu buryo bwo guhangana nabyo, nk'uko byatangajwe na Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS.
Dufite impungenge zikomeye cyane kubera ukuntu ibyo bitera impungenge kandi bikaba bikomeye, ndetse n'ukuntu ibikorwa by'iterabwoba bitinda.
Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iyi ndwara "itari bwigere ibaho".
Yavuze ko mu nyandiko CNN yasohoye muri Gashyantare, "uretse ibicurane, nta virusi y'ubuhumekero yigeze igaragara kuva igera ku isi kugeza ikwirakwizwa ku isi".
Ghebreyesus yavuze ko "tutigeze tubona icyorezo nk'icyatewe na coronavirus".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntitwigeze tubona icyorezo gihangayikishije abantu bose icyarimwe".
Iyi mibare mishya y'icyorezo ikurikiye icyemezo cya OMS cyo muri Mutarama cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cy'indwara z'ibyorezo ku isi.
Dr. Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'Amerika cyita ku ndwara zandura, yavuze ko iby'iki cyorezo "bizaba bibi kurushaho".
Kugeza ku wa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko nibura abantu 126.000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi, bigatuma abantu barenga 4.600 bapfa.
Icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019-2020 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) gikomeje kandi cyatewe na koronavirusi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikaze 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye i Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe nk'icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuzima rusange ku isi tariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020, cyemezwa nk'icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bahitana abagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Umubare w'abandura ubarirwa kuri 4% mu Bushinwa, naho ku isi hose ugera kuri 13.04% kugeza kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara harimo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ingorane zishobora kuba harimo pneumonia na syndrome yo guhumeka cyane.
Igihe cyo kuva ku isura y'umubiri kugeza igihe ibimenyetso byatangiriye, ubusanzwe ni nk'iminsi itanu, ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugera kuri cumi n'ine.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wihariye uvura virusi bizwi.
Ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ni ubuvuzi bw'ibimenyetso n'ubw'ubufasha. Ingamba z'ubutabazi zasabwe zirimo gukaraba intoki, gukorora, kugumana intera, no gukurikirana no kwigunga ku bantu bakekwaho kuba baranduye.
Abategetsi bo ku isi yose babyitabiriye bashyiraho ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo, gushyiraho za karantine, amasaha y'ijoro, kugenzura aho abantu bakorera, no gufunga amazu.
Icyorezo cyateye isi kudindira mu by'ubukungu, gusubika cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa by'umuco, politiki, idini, siporo, n'ibindi byinshi, bituma ubukene bwiyongera bitewe no kugura cyane.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu no ku rwego rw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cya 99,4% by'abanyeshuri ku isi.
Hari amakuru mabi kuri iyi virusi yakwirakwijwe ku mbuga za interineti, ndetse n'ibikorwa by'urwango rw'abanyamahanga no kurobanura Abashinwa, abantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Aziya, n'abantu bakomoka mu turere turimo abantu benshi banduye iyi virusi.
Kubera ko ingendo zagabanyijwe n'inganda zikomeye zafunzwe, imyuka ihumanya ikirere n'umwuka wa karuboni na yo yaragabanutse.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei), bwatangaje ko habonetse icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kandi ko iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Iyi mibare ijyanye ahanini n'isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, bityo ko virusi ishobora kuba ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.
Virusi yateje iki cyorezo yitwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi iherutse kuvumburwa kandi ifitanye isano na coronavirus y'igihuma, coronavirus y'inkorora, na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere w'indwara yaje kumenyekana arwaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi uwo muntu nta sano rifatika afite n'itsinda ry'amasoko y'amazi ryavuzwe nyuma.
Mu itsinda ry'abantu ba mbere batangajwe ko banduye mu kwezi kwa 12 mu 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse ko bifitanye isano n'iri soko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post cyavuze ko umuntu wa mbere ushobora kuba yanduye coronavirus ku wa 17 Ugushyingo 2019, akaba ari umugabo w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko, mu gihe ubwandu bushya bwagaragaye mu Bushinwa bwagabanutse, ariko bukaba bwiyongera mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze umubare w'abanduye mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Birashoboka ko hari umubare munini w'abantu batagaragazwa, cyane cyane mu bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abanduye wari uri mu rubyiruko, aho abantu bafite imyaka 19 n'abari munsi yayo bagize 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi hose. Umujyanama mukuru mu bya siyansi w'u Bwongereza, Patrick Vallance, agereranya ko 60% by'abaturage b'u Bwongereza bakeneye kwandura mbere y'uko ubudahangarwa bw'itsinda bushobora kugerwaho.
Abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe bagasanga baranduye COVID-19 hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoreye ibizamini abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho politiki yemewe yo kutagaragaza abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe bwerekanye ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abantu bagera kuri 86% banduye COVID-19 batagaragaye, kandi ko 79% by'abanduye banditswe ko banduye.
Ubushakashatsi bw'imibare bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 30 Werurwe bugaragaza ko imibare y'ubwandu mu Butaliyani iteganijwe kuba iri hejuru cyane ugereranyije n'umubare w'abamaze kwandura.
Igishushanyo mbonera cy'igihembwe cy'ibanze (R0) cya COVID-19 ni 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara, bwagaragaje ko uwo mubare ushobora kuba ari 5.7.
Abantu benshi barwaye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu batakira, igihe cyo kuva ku gukumira ibimenyetso kugeza ku gupfa kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, ariko akenshi ni iminsi 14.
Kuva ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97.000 bishwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 5 Gashyantare, hafi 80% by'abapfuye bari abantu bari hejuru y'imyaka 60 kandi 75% bari bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima by'imbere, birimo indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Imibare y'abapfuye mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange yerekeza ku bapfuye bapimwe bagasanga banduye COVID hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Imibare y'abishwe na COVID-19 ishobora kuba iri hejuru cyane, kubera ko imibare yemewe ishobora kuba idafite abantu bapfuye batagenzwe, urugero nk'abishwe bari mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku barwayi n'ahandi.
Ibaruramari ry'imibare y'abamaze gupfa mu Butaliyani ryerekanye ko umubare w'abamaze gupfa muri iki cyorezo uri hejuru y'uw'abamaze gupfa bitewe na COVID ku gipimo kiri hagati y'inshuro 4 na 5.
Umuvugizi w'umugore w'ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko "tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye watangajwe] ari muto ugereranyije n'umubare nyakuri", amagambo akomezwa n'ibarura ry'abantu ridafite aho rishingiye mu by'ubumenyi bwa siyansi muri Amerika.
Urupfu rwa mbere hanze y'Ubushinwa rwabaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho urupfu rwa mbere hanze ya Aziya rwabaye ku ya 14 Gashyantare mu Bufaransa.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'Ubushinwa, abantu barenga cumi bapfuye muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo n'Ubutaliyani.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu birenga mirongo ine n'intara z'ibihugu byamaze gutanga amakuru y'impfu, ku migabane yose, uretse Antarctica.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi igenda itandukana bitewe n'umubare w'abarwayi bapimwe, ubwiza bw'ubuzima, uburyo bwo kuvurwa, igihe cy'ubwandu bwa mbere, n'imiterere y'abaturage, urugero nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima muri rusange.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu mibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, igipimo cy'abapfuye ku isi hose cyari 6.0% (97.039/1.617.204) ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare w'abapfuye uratandukanye bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'abapfa n'abanduye yagabanutse kuva kuri 17.3% (ku bantu bagaragaye ku ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0.7% (ku bantu bagaragaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ubundi buryo bwo kubara ni umubare w'abapfa (CFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye bitewe n'indwara runaka, n'umubare w'abapfa bitewe n'ubwandu (IFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye bitewe n'indwara runaka (bafite cyangwa badafite).
Iyi mibare ntabwo ijyanye n'igihe kandi ikurikirana umubare w'abantu kuva ubwandu bugera ku barwayi kugeza igihe habonekeye umuti.
Hari intiti nyinshi zagerageje gukora imibare igaragaza ko abantu bafite ubwo burwayi.
Ikigo gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso cya Kaminuza ya Oxford, gitanga ingero z'abantu bapfa bitewe n'ubwandu muri rusange ziri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Uyu mupaka wo hejuru w'ibipimo by'ibipimo ujyana n'ibyavuye mu bipimo bya mbere byafashwe mu buryo butunguranye ku COVID-19 mu Budage no mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mibare y'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo bya CFR.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje ko icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cy'icyorezo n'igihe cy'imperuka ntibiramenyekana neza kandi gishobora gutandukana bitewe n'ahantu.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Penn State, yagize ati "mu gihe nta muntu urinda indwara, ubusanzwe ntiziyongera cyane, kandi zikarushaho kugabanuka iyo zidakomeje kugira abantu benshi.
Ariko kandi, biragoye cyane kugira ngo umuntu asobanukirwe neza igihe ibyo bizabera".
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi wa leta y'Ubushinwa, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko "icyorezo gishobora kurangira muri Kamena" mu gihe igihugu cyose cyaba cyashishikarijwe gukurikiza inama za OMS ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwizwa ry'iyi virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu Ishuri ry'Ubuziranenge n'Ubuvuzi bw'Akarere k'i Londres yavuze ko SRS-CoV-2 "izahora mu kirere, hashobora kuba hashize umwaka cyangwa ibiri".
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na kaminuza ya Imperial College, iyobowe na Neil Ferguson, abantu bagomba kwirinda kwikinisha no gufata izindi ngamba "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze (hashobora kumara amezi 18 cyangwa arenga) "
William Schaffner wa kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko bishoboka ko coronavirus, kubera ko yandura cyane, ishobora kuzimira burundu" kandi ko iyi ndwara "ishobora guhinduka indwara y'igihe, igaruka buri mwaka".
Ubukana bw'ubwongeye kubaho buzaba bushingiye ku bushobozi bw'uburwayi bw'itsinda ry'abantu n'ubukana bw'impinduka.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba atari bimwe kandi umuntu wayanduye ashobora kuba nta bimenyetso agaragaza.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'inkorora yumye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara ni umunaniro, guturika kw'imyanya y'ubuhumekero (phlegm), guhomba, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo no mu ngingo, kuribwa mu muhogo, kurwara umutwe, kugira isesemi, kuruka, kurwara amaraso, kuruka, kuruka, kurwara mu nda, cyangwa kurwara indwara y'impyiko. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) rivuga ko umuntu umwe kuri batandatu aba afite uburwayi bukomeye kandi ko guhumeka bimugora.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyanditse ibimenyetso byihutirwa birimo guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'igihimba cyangwa ububabare bw'igihimba, guhungabana, kugorana kugenda, no guhinduka ubururu mu maso no ku minwa; byihutirwa kwitabwaho n'abaganga mu gihe ibi bimenyetso bibonetse.
Abantu bamwe na bamwe banduye bashobora kuba bafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, ariko bakagaragaza ko banduye, ni yo mpamvu abashakashatsi batanga inama ko abantu bahuye n'abanduye bagombye gukurikiranwa cyane kandi bakagenzurwa kugira ngo barebe ko banduye.
Abashinwa bavuga ko imibare y'abapfa ari mike cyane, ku buryo ishobora kugera kuri 44%.
Igihe cyo kubyara (igihe hagati y'ubwandu n'intangiriro y'ibimenyetso) gikunze kuba hagati y'iminsi 1 na 14, akenshi iminsi 5. Urugero rw'ibidashoboka, raporo y'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 babuze ubushobozi bwo kumva amahumbezi yabanje kuba 30%, hanyuma biza kugabanuka kugeza 15%.
Ibisobanuro birambuye ku buryo iyi ndwara yandura biracyari mu bushakashatsi.
Ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 rifatwa ko riterwa cyane cyane n'abantu bahuye hafi kandi bakoresheje uduce duto dutangwa n'umuntu ukorora, witsamura cyangwa uvuga; abantu bahuye hafi ni abantu bari hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (3 na 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukorora udukorosi tutariho umuti bishobora gutuma utu turemangingo tuva muri metero 4,5 (metero 15) tukagera kuri metero 8,2 (metero 27).
Abashakashatsi bamwe batekereza ko virusi ishobora kwanduzwa n'utuntu duto tumara igihe kirekire mu kirere kandi tugaragazwa n'amagambo.
Utwo duce dushobora kugwa mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'umuntu uri hafi yayo, cyangwa ugasanga twahumetse mu bihaha.
Bimwe mu bikorwa byo kwa muganga, urugero nko gutera intanga no guhumeka umutima, bishobora gutuma ibyo umuntu ataka bihinduka umwuka maze bigakwirakwira mu mwuka.
Nanone umuntu ashobora kwandura iyo akoze ku bintu byanduye, harimo uruhu, maze akabikora ku maso, ku mazuru no ku munwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko virusi ishobora gukwirakwira mu isuku, iki gihangayikishije ni uko bishoboka ko nta cyo yaba.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yateye utwatsi ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu kanwa binyuze mu myanya y'urwagashya. Iyi virusi yandurira cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere umuntu agize ibimenyetso, nubwo ishobora gukwirakwira mbere y'uko umuntu agaragaza ibimenyetso by'uburwayi no mu gihe indwara imaze kuba ndende.
Abantu bapimwa basanga baranduye mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara biboneka, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko umuntu ashobora kuba yanduye mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara biboneka.
Hari raporo nke cyane z'abanduye zemejwe na laboratwari, ariko ubwandu bw'abantu butari bwagaragaye bwagaragaye mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi bwo gushakisha abantu bahuye n'ubwandu.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitamenyekanye neza uburyo bworoshye iyi ndwara yandurira, umuntu umwe ashobora kwanduza abandi babiri cyangwa batatu.
By'umwihariko, byaragaragaye ko virusi ishobora kugaragara mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu ku iplastiki (polypropylene) na 304 ibyuma bidakomeye, umunsi umwe ku ikarito, n'amasaha arenga ane ku muringa.
Ariko kandi, ibi biratandukana bitewe n'ubuhehere n'ubushyuhe. Amatungo n'andi matungo byapimishijwe ko afite COVID-19.
Nta gihamya igaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu virusi, nubwo abategetsi bo mu Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, nko gukorana n'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye.
Koronavirusi y'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya, ya mbere yabonetse mu bantu batatu bari bafite umusonga uhuriranye n'icyorezo cyo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero cya Wuhan.
Ibimenyetso byose bya virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano na koronavirusi yo mu bidukikije. Inyuma y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi ishobora gusenyuka iyo igaragaye mu isabune yo mu rugo, igabanya ubwirinzi bwayo. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya hafi na SARS-CoV yo mu itangira.
Virusi byitezwe ko ifite inkomoko ku nyamaswa.
Isesengura ry'imiterere y'umubiri ryerekanye ko coronavirus ifite ikinyabuzima cy'ubwoko bwa Betacoronavirus, mu bwoko bwa Scovarbeirus (umurongo wa B) hamwe n'imitwe ibiri y'ubwoko bw'ingurube.
Iyi virusi ifite 96% by'ubwisanzure muri genome yose n'indi mikorobe ya coronavirus (BatCov RaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi bo mu Bushinwa basanze hari ikinyuranyo cy'amino asidi imwe gusa mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'imiterere ya genome hagati ya virusi ya dengue na virusi y'umuntu.
Kugeza ubu, igereranya ry'ibinyabuzima byose ryagaragaje ko hari 92% by'ubwoko bw'inzoka ya korona bw'ingore na SARS-CoV-2, ibyo bikaba bidahagije kugira ngo bigaragaze ko ingore ari zo zanduye SARS-CoV-2.
Indwara ya virusi ishobora gusuzumwa hakoreshejwe ibimenyetso, ariko amaherezo igemezwa hakoreshejwe ikinyabupfura cya transcriptase polymerase (RT-PCR) cyangwa se hakoreshejwe tomography ya CT.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan bugereranya porogaramu za PCR na CT, bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo kugenzura neza kurusha PCR, ariko ikaba idafite ubushobozi bwo kugaragaza ibimenyetso byihariye, bitewe n'uko ibipimo by'ibipimo byinshi by'ibipimo by'indwara y'ibyorezo n'izindi ndwara.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe ibijyanye n'imikorere y'indwara z'indwara z'imitsi, cyatanze inama igira iti "ibipimo bya CT ntibikwiye gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igisubizo cya mbere mu gusuzuma COVID-19".
OMS yasohoye amabwiriza yo gupima RNA kuri SARS-CoV-2, yatangajwe bwa mbere ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Ibizamini bikoresha uburyo bwo gupima mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR).
Ibipimo bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso.
Ibisubizo ubusanzwe biboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi mike.
Muri rusange, iki gipimo gikoreshwa mu gupima umura, ariko umura ushobora no gukoreshwa. Laboratwari nyinshi n'ibigo byinshi birimo gukora ibipimo bya seroloji bibona abasirikare b'umubiri.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri ibyo bizamini by'imiti cyagaragaye ko gifite ukuri ku buryo cyemewe gukoreshwa cyane.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibizamini bya serological byakozwe na Cellex byemewe gukoresha byihutirwa, gusa n'ibigo byemewe.
Bimwe mu biranga isura ya radiographie na tomographie igaragaye (CT) ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso harimo ubukana bw'ibirahure by'ibumoso bw'igice cyo mu nda kandi nta efusi ya pleura.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ubuvuzi bw'urumuri mu Butaliyani ririmo gukora urubuga mpuzamahanga rwo kuvura abarwayi bemejwe.
Kubera ko hari izindi ndwara zandura, urugero nka adenovirus, gufata amashusho nta PCR yemeza bifite ubushobozi buke bwo kumenya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bunini bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bwagereranyije ibizamini bya CT byo mu gatuza n'ibya PCR kandi bwerekana ko nubwo bidasanzwe ku bwandu, ibipimo by'ibishushanyo by'ubwandu bwihuse kandi byumva neza ku buryo byashishikarizwaga ko byakwifashishwa mu gusuzuma ubwandu mu duce dutuwe n'icyorezo.
Imikorere y'imikorere y'imashini ikoranabuhanga ikorana n'imikorere y'imikorere y'imashini ikorana n'ikoranabuhanga (AI) y'imashini ikora imikorere y'imashini ikorana n'imashini ikora imashini ikora imashini ikora ikoranabuhanga (AI) ikoreshwa mu gupima virusi ikora kuri radiyo na CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda ikwirakwizwa ry'iyi ndwara harimo kugira isuku nziza, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa mbere yo gukaraba intoki, no kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe ukorora cyangwa witsamuye ndetse no guhita utura agapfukamunwa mu myanda.
Abantu bashobora kuba baranduye bagirwa inama yo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari ahantu hahurira abantu benshi.
Ingamba zo guhagarika imbangukiragutabara zirakenewe kandi kugirango wirinde ikwirakwira. Guverinoma mu turere dutandukanye zagabanyije cyangwa zasabye guhagarika ingendo zose zidakenewe zijya no mu bihugu n'uturere twibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Nyamara, virusi yageze ku rwego rwo gukwirakwira mu baturage mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi yakwirakwiriye mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho bayanduye cyangwa uko bayanduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima budafite aho babogamiye bakorera abantu bashobora kuba baranduye bagirwa inama yo gukoresha ingamba zo kwirinda, kwirinda guhura, no kurinda amaso.
Gukoresha amakuru y'ahantu kuri telefoni muri leta muri ibyo bikorwa byateje impungenge ku mutekano w'ikiremwamuntu, Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 isaba ko ayo makuru yajya ahagarikwa.
Hakozwe cyangwa hashyizweho porogaramu zitandukanye za terefone zigendanwa, kandi kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere arenga icumi akora ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugirango umenye aho uwegereye undi terefone.
Ikindi ni uko abakoresha uru rubuga bazajya bahabwa ubutumwa bugaragaza niba hari umuntu wahuye na we akaba yaranduye COVID-19. Hari n'amazimwe menshi ajyanye n'uburyo bwo kwirinda kwanduza; urugero, gukaraba mu mazuru no kwisiga umuti wo gukaraba mu matako ntibikora.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 ruraboneka, nubwo hari imiryango myinshi irimo gukora ku buryo rwaboneka.
Gukaraba intoki birashishikarizwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
CDC isaba ko abantu bakaraba intoki kenshi n'isabune n'amazi mu gihe cy'amasegonda nibura makumyabiri, cyane cyane nyuma yo kuva ku musarane cyangwa igihe intoki zisa n'izanduye; mbere yo kurya; na nyuma yo guhanagura, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Ibi ni ukubera ko, hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yicibwa na savon yo mu rugo yangiza urwungano rwayo.
Ikindi kandi, CDC isaba gukoresha imiti yo guhanagura intoki ikurikije inzoga, ifite nibura 60% by'inzoga ku bwinshi, mu gihe isabune n'amazi bidahari.
OMS ivuga ko abantu batagomba gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa mbere yo gukaraba intoki.
Umusozo ushobora guhanagurwa ukoresheje umuti (mu minota imwe yo kwisiga umuti wica udukoko ku gisenge cy'icyuma), harimo etanol 6271%, isopropanol 50100%, sodium hypochlorite 0.1%, hydrogen peroxide 0.5%, na povidone-iodine 0.27.5%.
Izindi nk'ibisukari bya benzalkonium chloride na chlorhexidine gluconate, ntibikora neza.
CDC isaba ko mu gihe hari umuntu ukekwaho cyangwa wemejwe ko afite COVID muri rusange, nko mu biro cyangwa mu bigo by'abana, ahantu hose, nko mu biro, mu byumba by'isuku, ahantu abantu bahurira, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bakoresha nk'imashini za tablets, za touch screen, za keyboard, za remote control na za ATM zikoreshwa n'abantu bafite COVID, bigomba kwanduzwa.
Imiryango irebana n'ubuzima igira inama abantu ko mu gihe bakoroye cyangwa batose, bagombye gutwikira izuru n'umunwa cyangwa bagakoresha agafuka, hanyuma bakaza kujugunya ako kanya.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi turasabwa cyane cyane ku bantu bashobora kuba baranduye kubera ko twashyize imipaka ku bwinshi no ku buryo bworoshye bwo guhumeka utwo dupfukamunwa mu gihe umuntu avuze, ahumeka cyangwa akoroye.
OMS yatanze amabwiriza y'igihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Nk'uko byemezwa na Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ibyifuzo by'abantu byo gukora ku maso n'amaboko adahumanye, ari na byo bikunze guteza ubwandu".
OMS isaba ko abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza bakoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe gusa bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, urugero nk'abitaho abantu barwaye COVID-19, nubwo OMS yemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda kwikora ku maso.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC isaba gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi dukoreshwa mu buvuzi dukorwa mu mwenda. Ubushinwa bwasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi dukoreshwa rimwe, cyane cyane igihe bari hafi y'abandi bantu (1 metero) (3 cyangwa munsi).
Hong Kong isaba ko kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe uri mu modoka zitwara abantu benshi cyangwa igihe uri ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima muri Thailand, bagiriye abantu inama yo gukora udupfukamunwa tw'imyenda mu ngo zabo kandi bakajya tuyuhagira buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Czech na Slovakia yabujije abaturage bayo gusohoka ahantu hahurira abantu benshi batambaye udupfukamunwa cyangwa utw'imbere.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abaturage bayo bose kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bari ahantu hahurira abantu benshi kugira ngo birinde bo ubwabo ndetse n'abandi.
Leta ya Otirishiya isaba buri wese winjiye muri serivisi kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Isiraheli yasabye abaturage bayo kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe bari mu ruhame.
Tayiwani, ihora ikora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi kuva hagati muri Werurwe, yasabye abagenzi bakora muri za gari ya moshi na za bisi zo mu mujyi kwambara udupfukamunwa guhera ku ya 1 Mata.
Panama isaba abantu kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe cyose bavuye mu rugo, kandi igasaba ko hakorwa udupfukamunwa tw'imbere ku bantu batabasha kugura udupfukamunwa.
Udupfukamunwa tw'amaso kandi dukoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Maleziya na Singapuru.
Gahunda yo kwirinda (n'indi bitaga ihagarikwa ry'umubiri) ni uburyo bwo kwirinda ubwandu bugamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya abantu kugirana imishyikirano ya bugufi.
Uburyo bwo gukumira imyitwarire mibi mu baturage bukubiyemo gukumira abantu mu ngo zabo; gukumira ingendo; gufunga amashuri, aho bakorera, amakinamico, amazu y'imikino cyangwa amaduka.
Abantu bashobora gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda gusabana baguma mu rugo, bagabanya ingendo, bakirinda kujya ahantu hari abantu benshi, bakoresha induru zitari ukubana, kandi bagakomeza gutandukanya.
Muri iki gihe, leta nyinshi zasabye abantu kwirinda mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Umubare w'abantu bashoboraga guhurira hamwe, wabaga uteganijwe n'inzego za leta ya Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima, wahise ugabanuka, uva ku bantu 250 (mu gihe nta bantu bari bazi ko mu gace runaka hari COVID-19), ugera kuri 50, nyuma ugera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, u Budage yabujije iteraniro mu duce rusange ririmwo abantu barenga babiri. Abasaza n'abantu bafite indwara z'ibyorezo nka diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso, n'abashyize imbaraga z'umubiri mu kaga ko kwandura indwara zikomeye no kugira ibibazo byinshi, CDC itera inkunga abantu kuguma mu ngo zabo igihe cyose bishoboka mu turere turimo icyorezo cy'icyorezo. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima batangiye guhindura imvugo "gukumira abantu mu buryo bw'imibereho" bakayihindura "gukumira abantu mu buryo bw'umubiri", kugira ngo basobanure ko intego ari ukugabanya guhura n'abantu mu buryo bworoshye, haba mu buryo bw'umubiri cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwirinda mu mibanire" bitera abantu gutekereza ko bagomba kwigunga byuzuye kandi ntibatere abantu inkunga yo gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi binyuze mu bundi buryo. Inzego zimwe na zimwe zashyizeho amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri iyo nama harimo ko ugomba gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ubana nawe gusa kandi udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Abantu basuzumwe COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuba baranduye, basabwe kwigunga mu rugo.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwigunga. Guverinoma nyinshi zisaba cyangwa zisaba ko abantu bose batuye mu turere twibasiwe na virusi ya corona bagomba kwigunga.
Amabwiriza yo kwishyira mu kato akomeye cyane, agenewe abantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragaragaweho n'indwara ya COVID-19 n'abantu baheruka kujya mu bihugu cyangwa uturere turimo COVID-19 yandura, bagirwa inama yo kwishyira mu kato k'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bagaragaweho bwa nyuma.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo ni uguhagarika cyangwa gukandamiza, no kugabanya.
Gukingira abantu bikorwa mu bihe by'intangiriro by'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu banduye no gushyira mu bikorwa izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu no gukingira bigamije guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu baturage bose.
Iyo bitagishoboka guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara, hakurikiraho imihati yo kugabanya: ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka ku nzego z'ubuvuzi no ku baturage.
Gukora ibikorwa byo gukumira no kugabanya bishobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira bisaba ingamba zikomeye cyane zo guhindura icyorezo mu buryo bwo kugabanya umubare w'abasangwa ku kigero cyo munsi ya 1. Kimwe mu byo kurwanya indwara zandura ni ukugerageza kugabanya igihe cy'icyorezo, ibyo bikaba byitwa kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo.
Ibyo byagabanya ibyago byo kurengerwa n'ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo no kuvura.
Ingamba zitari iz'imiti mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo zirimo ingamba z'umuntu ku giti cye, nk'isuku yo mu ntoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwigenga; ingamba zo mu rwego rw'abaturage zigamije gukumira imyitwarire y'abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa by'amakoraniro; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwakira no kwitabira ubu buryo bwo kwitabira; n'ingamba zo mu rwego rw'ibidukikije, nko gusukura imiterere. Izindi ngamba zikomeye zigamije gukumira iki cyorezo zashyizweho mu Bushinwa mu gihe ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bugenda bugaragara, nko gufunga umujyi wose no guhagarika ingendo.
Ibihugu byinshi na byo byashyizeho ingamba zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho igenzura ry'imbaga n'ikigo cy'imiyoborere, ndetse inatangaza ko abantu banduye bagomba kwimuka.
Singapuru itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku banduye bakwitandukanya kandi igaca ibihano bikomeye ku bantu batabikora.
Taiwan yatangiranye ibikorwa byo gukora udupfukamunwa kandi ihana ababika ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Imikino yo mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika yerekana ko kugabanya (gucika intege, ariko ntibikabuza ikwirakwizwa ry'icyorezo) no gukumira (guhindura iterambere ry'icyorezo) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ihungabana ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abajya kwa muganga ku kigero cya kabiri n'uw'abapfa ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, ariko ikomeza gutuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa, n'uburyo bwo kwivuza bukagabanuka.
Gucika birashoboka, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikiri mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza urukingo rubonetse, niba ari rwo rwa mbere rubonetse), kuko bitabaye ibyo, ubwandu buziyongera vuba igihe ingamba zo gucika zizaba zarangiye.
Gahunda z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo zagize ingaruka ku bukungu no ku mibereho y'abaturage.
Nta miti yihariye yo kurwanya COVID-19 yemewe, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuyikoraho, harimo no gupima imiti isanzwe.
Kunywa imiti ya kanyanga, kunywa amazi ahagije no kuruhuka bihagije bishobora kugufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso by'ibicurane.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo, umuntu ashobora gukenera imiti ya ogisijeni, imiti y'ubutabazi bw'amaraso mu mishipure ndetse n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Gukoresha cyane cyane imiti ya 'steroid' bishobora gutuma umurwayi arushaho kuremba.
