Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yongereyeho amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo ku Bwami bw'Ubwongereza na Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe by'amage kugira ngo amafaranga ya leta aboneke mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi byinshi muri Amerika byafunze cyangwa byagabanyije amasaha yo gukora mu rwego rwo kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari kimaze kwemezwa muri leta 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, umujyi wa New York wari ufite abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri wa New York yavuze ko ingamba z'imibereho zisa n'izigenda neza kuko umubare w'abandura wiyongeraga kabiri, ukava ku minsi 2,0 ugera kuri 4,7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32,308 bari bamaze kwandura icyorezo cya Coronavirus mu mujyi wa New York, naho abantu 672 barapfuye. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje ko ifite abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu cyose ku isi, harimo n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku ya 8 Mata, hari abantu 400.335 bari bamaze kwandura icyorezo cya Coronavirus muri Amerika, naho abantu 12,841 barapfuye.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibitangazamakuru ku ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera ingamba zo kwirinda kugera ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, USNS Comfort, ubwato bw'ibitaro bufite ibitanda 1000, bwashyize i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yari ifite abantu 884 bapfuye mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, abantu barenga 100,000 banduye ku ya 3 Mata. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kuba byaragabanyije ibyago no kugenzura ubutumwa binyuze mu kuyobora abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza imvugo n'ibitabo by'ibanze bijyanye na virusi mu biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Muri rusange, Trump yari yemeye ko habaho imyanzuro igamije gukemura ibibazo by'ubukungu.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenga Amerika kuba yishingikiriza ku bicuruzwa by'ingenzi by'Ubushinwa, birimo ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Isesengura ry'ingendo zo mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura ingendo z'abantu kandi ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'amakuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yatanzwe n'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Ibyogajuru, abantu benshi bavuye i Wuhan bari muri Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne nabyo byavuzwe ko ari ahantu hazwi cyane ku bantu bava i Wuhan.
Bali ni cyo gihugu cya mbere cyatangaje ko cyiteguye mu mijyi 20 izwi cyane, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yo yagaragaje ko yiteguye cyane.
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bitaramenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Ositaraliya izashyira ingufu ku kugenzura imipaka no ku itumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, Ositaraliya yatangaje ko havutse ikibazo cyo kwihanganira ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei hashyizweho ingamba zo gushyira mu kato ingendo rusange, ibihugu byinshi birateganya kwimura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri utwo duce, cyane cyane hakoreshejwe indege ihabwa igihugu cy'inkomoko, byemerewe n'abayobozi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, u Buyapani, u Buhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Arijantine, u Budage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu byatangiye gukora gahunda yo guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakistani yavuze ko itazagira icyo ikora ngo irungike abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Brezili yahunze abantu 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa abo mu miryango yabo, hiyongeraho abantu bane b'Abanyapolonye, Umushinwa n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage ba Polonye, u Bushinwa n'u Buhinde baroherejwe muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brezili yahagaze mbere yo gukomeza urugendo mu gihugu cya Brezili.
Abanyabrezili bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yakodeshejwe na leta ya Amerika) bavuye muri Wuhan berekezwa ahitwa Trenton CFB mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abantu 185 bavuye muri Wuhan bagana muri CFB Trenton.
Abayobozi ba Australia bavanye abaturage 277 babo ku ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare bajyanwa mu Kirwa cya Natal, aho bamaze iminsi 14 bakorera mu kato.
Indege y'abatabazi bavuye muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi (barimo bamwe bavuye muri Ositaraliya no muri Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Whangaparoa, kiri mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gutahukana Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bamaze kuvanwa muri Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gutahukana abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari ikodeshejwe na leta y'Afurika y'Epfo yagarukanye abanyamahanga 112.
Ibizamini by'ubuvuzi byakozwe mbere y'uko indege igenda, maze abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus barigumishwa kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo bonyine bageragejwe bagaragaza ko banduye ni bo basubijwe mu bihugu byabo.
Nyuma y'ibizamini, abantu bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, barimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abapilote, abakozi bo mu mahoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi, bashyizwe mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraq kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusiya, Pakisitani, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zitandukanye zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu kohereza imfashanyo mu Bushinwa mu turere twazahajwe n'icyorezo, hamwe n'itsinda ry'abakozi bo mu mujyi wa Chicago; bivugwa ko bagejeje udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi bw'abantu Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 n'ibindi bikoresho byo kwirinda, birimo n'intoki n'imyenda, binyuze mu modoka y'indege y'ubutabazi ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union Hospital ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ku muryango w'isi yose wita ku buzima (WHO) mu gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo no mu rwego rwo kurinda "abantu bafite ibyago muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200.000 kuri Philippines ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yoherereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni $2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwoherereje Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho byo kwa muganga, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'imiti i Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze miliyoni 18 z'intoki zo kwa muganga mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwoherereje u Bushinwa ibikoresho byo kwa muganga birimo imyenda ya Hazmat 10.000, na Amerika yohereje toni 17.8 z'imiti yo kwa muganga mu Bushinwa kandi isezeranya inkunga y'inyongera ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu rwego rw'ubufasha bw'amafaranga ku bihugu byibasiwe.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'inzobere mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho bigera kuri miliyoni 1.1 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6, n'imyenda 60,000 yo kwikingira i Addis Ababa, muri Ethiopia, ngo bihabwe Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yo kohereza muri Panama ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi 5.000, udupfukamunwa 100.000 n'ibyuma bitanu byo guhumeka.
Ma yatanze kandi ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Kanada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Czech byagaragaje impungenge ku ireme ry'amaske n'ibikoresho by'igerageza byakozwe n'Abashinwa.
Urugero, Esipanye yahagaritse ibikoresho 58 000 by'ibizamini bya coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30% gusa; mu gihe u Buholandi bwahagaritse udupfukamunwa 600 000 tw'ibizamini byakozwe n'Ubushinwa dufite amakosa.
U Bubiligi nabwo bwafashe udupfukamunwa 100.000 tudakoreshwa, twibeshya ko ari utw'Ubushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri ni utw'Abanyakolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'Ubushinwa bwitabiriwe neza mu bice bimwe bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa byihutirwa byo gufasha ibihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimagije leta y'Ubushinwa ku bushake bwayo mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
OMS ivuga ko hari itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004 ubwo abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga guhisha amakuru ku buryo bibuza ingamba zo kwirinda no gukumira, n'ikibazo cy'ubutegetsi bw'i Burayi "bujya bujya buvugurura amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo hirindwe ubwoba mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru y'Ubunani".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu kwamagana icyemezo cya leta y'ibanze cyo guhagarika ingendo i Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko atari inama ya OMS", ariko ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo kwiyemeza guhashya icyorezo aho icyorezo cyibasiye cyane" kandi ko "bitari byarigeze bibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu banduye hanze y'Ubushinwa kandi umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu wiyongereye, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'abantu ku isi (PHEIC), ari cyo cyorezo cya gatandatu cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'abantu ku isi (PHEIC) kuva cyatangira mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC ari "akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite ubukene n'ubukene bwo hagati, bidafite inzego z'ubuzima zihagije.
Mu gusubiza ku iyubahirizwa ry'ibihano by'ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zibuza ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga bitari ngombwa" kandi ko "OMS idatangaza ko ingendo n'ubwiyunge bigabanywa".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari azakoreshwa mu gushyigikira ingamba zo guhangana n'icyorezo mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi mu gihe icyorezo cyakwirakwizwa".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "imbaraga zacu ziganisha ku gice cy'ubudahangarwa" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura amafaranga menshi nyuma". Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara y'iyi virusi.
Ku munsi umwe, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye António Guterres yemeye gutanga "igisubizo cyo gukoresha imbaraga zose z'umuryango w'abibumbye".
Nyuma, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wahise ukora Itsinda ry'Imicungire y'Ibibazo kugira ngo rishobore guhuza igisubizo cyose cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, aho OMS yavuze ko bizatuma "bashobora kwibanda ku gusubiza mu by'ubuzima, mu gihe ibindi bigo bishobora gukoresha ubumenyi bwabyo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo mu mibereho rusange, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba OMS n'ab'amahanga bo mu Bushinwa bari ku rwego rw'igihugu bashyizwe mu bikorwa; iyo itsinda yari ifite intego yo gutanga impuguke mpuzamahanga na OMS mu Bushinwa mu rwego rwo gufasha mu gucunga indwara zo mu gihugu no gusuzuma "uburemere n'ikwirakizura ry'indwara" binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa no guhura n'inzego z'igihugu, no gusura ku rwego rwo gusuzuma "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo kurwanya indwara ku rwego rw'intara n'uturere, birimo imijyi n'icyaro". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus" kandi ko, nubwo byari hakiri kare kuvuga ko ari icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kuba "mu cyiciro cyo kwitegura".
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza icyorezo cya coronavirus cyateye muri Iran, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'ubushakashatsi muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo ryigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ingamba z'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi zizazamuka kuva ku rwego rwo hejuru cyane, iki kikaba ari cyo kigero cyo hejuru cy'ubushishozi n'ibyago.
Mu itangazo ryashyizwe ahagaragara na Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'Umuryango Mpuzamahanga w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye yo kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo, yatanze umuburo ugira uti "iki ni cyo gihe buri butegetsi bwose bwo kuri iyi si bugomba guhangana n'ukuri: Mukomeze kuba maso.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuza iwawe kandi ugomba kwitegura", kandi akomeza avuga ko ingamba z'ubutabazi zikwiye zafasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane kurusha ibindi".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemerera inzego z'ubuzima gutangaza icyorezo cy'isi yose, avuga ko gutangaza ibi bivuze ko "byanze bikunze twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya koronavirusi ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'umubare uteye ubwoba w'ubwandu n'ubukana, ndetse n'uburebure butera ubwoba bw'ibikorwa". OMS yahawe impaka zikomeye kubera ko itari ifite ubushobozi buhagije mu guhangana n'icyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima bw'abaturage no kugenzura ko virusi ari icyorezo.
Bimwe mu byakozwe harimo inyandiko y'ubusabe yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku ya 6 Mata, yandikiwe Tedros Adhanom, Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, asaba ko yegura.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'ikiremwamuntu z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zatangaje ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bugomba kubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Uwo mutwe w'abahanga wavuze ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira ku bufasha bukiza ubuzima bwe kandi ko leta ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima budashobora gukoreshwa nk'impamvu yo kuvangura itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abantu bo mu moko make, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi zo mu gihugu, abatagira aho baba, abafite ubukene bukabije, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bakeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga y'ubutegetsi irimo gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo ihangane n'ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage bya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubutwererane n'Iterambere watangije gahunda yo gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi yuzuye ku bisubizo bya politiki mu bihugu byose ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Guhera kuri politiki zo gukomeza inganda z'ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'akato k'uturere n'ingendo, ihuriro ry'ikoranabuhanga ririmo urukurikirane rw'amategeko y'ibihugu, rigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bundi buryo no korohereza igisubizo ku isi hose mu guhangana n'ibibazo bya coronavirus.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yakomeje kunengwa na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, ku bijyanye n'uburyo iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi bo mu rwego rw'intara mu ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa (CPC) bahagaritswe mu gihe bari mu bikorwa byo gushyiraho gahunda ya guma mu rugo mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, mu kugaragaza ko batishimiye uburyo inzego za politiki zagiye zikemura icyorezo muri ako karere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bemeza ko iki cyemezo kigamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti mu Bushinwa Xi Jinping kugira ngo adateza umujinya mu ruhame ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira igitekerezo cy'uko COVID-19 yakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Guverinoma ya Amerika Donald Trump yise coronavirus "virus y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "virus ya Wuhan" avuga ko "ibikorwa by'igitsure by'Ubushinwa byongereye imbaraga virusi ihindutse icyorezo cy'isi".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyabonye ubutumwa bwa leta ya Amerika bugaragaza uburyo bwo gushyikirana kandi bigaragara ko bwaturutse mu nama y'umutekano, ubwo buryo bwiswe "Byose byerekeye Ubushinwa.
Twahawe itegeko ryo kugerageza no kugeza ubu butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo imbonerahamwe z'abanyamakuru na televiziyo".Ibitangazamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byemeza ko ingamba z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe n'iyi virusi ari igice cy'ibinyoma cyo kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umukuru w'inzego z'ibanze w'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Josep Borrell, yatanze umuburo avuga ko hari "ikindi gice cya politiki y'isi, harimo kurwanira kugira icyo kigeraho binyuriye mu guhinduranya ukuri no 'guhanahana ibitekerezo.'"
Borrell kandi yavuze ko, "Ubushinwa bushaka cyane ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari abafatanyabikorwa bafite inshingano kandi bizerwa".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ndetse bivugwa ko bwoherereje ibihugu bibiri bya nyuma imfashanyo.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'udupfukamunwa 100,000 yahawe na Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano by'Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Amerika na bo barashinjwa ko batanze imfashanyo yari igenewe ibindi bihugu ikajya mu byabo.
Hari kandi amakimbirane yo kwambara udupfukamunwa bivugwa ko ari hagati y'ibindi bihugu, nka u Budage, Otirishiya, u Busuwisi; hamwe na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Turukiya kandi yafashe ibyuma bihumeka umuriro by'amashanyarazi byari bigenewe Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi utagira ubufatanye n'Ubutaliyani bugarijwe n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bwonyine ari bwo bwitabiriye imishyikirano hagati y'ibihugu byombi.
Birumvikana ko ibyo bidashimishije ku Banyaburayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kwakira telefoni iturutse ku Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yohereje ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza mu Butaliyani abaganga b'igisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo kurwanya indwara, n'ibindi bikoresho byo mu buvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo yavuzwe n'umuntu utazwi wari "umutware mu bya politiki wo ku rwego rwo hejuru", wavuze ko 80 ku ijana by'ubufasha bw'u Burusiya "nta cyo bwagirira u Butaliyani".
Iyi nkunga yashinje Uburusiya ko bwakoze ibitero by'ubushake "bya politiki n'ibya dipolomasi".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, birengagije ibyo bitangazamakuru kandi bagaragaza ko bashimira.
U Burusiya kandi bwoherereje Amerika indege irimo imfashanyo z'ubuvuzi.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "igihe Putin yatangaga ubufasha kuri bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, yatekerezaga ko niba hari abakora ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho byo muri Amerika babonye uburyo, na bo bashoboraga kubwishyura mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu by'Uburayi na Baltique, ikaba ari imyitozo ya gisirikare ikomeye cyane NATO yakoze kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izaba ku rwego ruto.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango uharanira ikurwaho ry'intwaro za kirimbuzi Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Muri iki gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange, iyi myitozo ntabwo ibangamiye ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi byitabiriye gusa, ahubwo n'abaturage bo mu bihugu bikoreramo". Leta ya Irani yibasiwe cyane n'iyi virusi, aho abanyamuryango b'inteko bagera kuri cumi n'abiri banduye hamwe n'abanyapolitiki cumi na batanu bahoze cyangwa bariho.
Ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yanditse ibaruwa ifunguye asaba abayobozi b'isi ubufasha avuga ko igihugu cye kigerageza kurwanya icyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyateye inkunga Amerika yo gufata politiki z'imibereho rusange zisanzwe mu bindi bihugu bikize, zirimo ubuvuzi rusange, ubwisungane mu kwita ku bana, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango cyishyurwa, n'ibipimo biri hejuru by'amafaranga yo kwita ku buzima rusange.
Abasesengura politiki batekereza ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku amahirwe ya Donald Trump yo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida yo mu 2020.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "ibikorwa by'abashakashatsi b'Ubuyapani byo guhagarika abantu mu buryo budasobanutse kandi budafite intego" nyuma yuko Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uvuye muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri ahantu hateganyijwe na leta.
Mu ntangiriro, abantu bo muri Koreya y'Epfo ntibari bemeranya ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in azafata iki kibazo.
Abenshi mu baturage ba Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko, haba mu gusaba ko Moon asonerwa, hashingiwe ku byo bavuga ko leta yakoze nabi mu guhangana n'icyorezo, cyangwa mu gushimira uko yabyitwayemo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagaragaje impungenge z'uko byatuma guverinoma ikomeza kugira ububasha.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko y'icyo gihugu yahisemo kwemerera Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orbán gutegeka binyuze mu mategeko atagira ingengabihe, ihagarika inteko no guhagarika amatora, no guhana abantu bafatwa nk'abahimbye amakuru y'ibinyoma ku byerekeye virusi n'uburyo leta yakemuye ibibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, cyatewe n'ubwiyongere bw'ibikoresho bikoreshwa ku isi mu kurwanya icyorezo, gucuruza mu buryo bwo guhangayika, no guhagarika imikorere y'inganda n'ibikorwa byo mu rwego rwa logistique.
Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura ibiribwa n'imiti muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abakiriya biyongera cyane kandi abatanga ibyo bikoresho bakabura aho bakorera.
Hari n'uturere twagize ikibazo cy'ubucuruzi buturutse ku mpungenge yatumye habaho kubura ibyangombwa nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yo mu macupa, bituma habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho.
By'umwihariko, inganda z'ikoranabuhanga zatangaje ko hari igihe cyo gutumiza ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga mu buryo butari bwo.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, umubare w'abantu bakeneye ibikoresho byo kwirinda, wikubye incuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byikuba inshuro 20 z'ibisanzwe, bituma inganda zitanga imiti zihagarika imirimo yazo mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Ibi kandi byatumye habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho birinda abantu kwanduza umubiri ku isi, OMS ikaba irakangurira abantu ko ibi bishobora gushyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'abaganga.
Muri Australia, icyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bagurisha daigou kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Australia mu Bushinwa.
Ibi bikorwa byatumye amata y'ifu abura mu masoko menshi, birangira guverinoma ya Ositaraliya yarabujije. Nubwo mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan habonetse abarwayi benshi ba COVID-19, n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, utwo turere twombi twirinze ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani byafashe zo kurwanya ububiko no gucuruza mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko ibintu by'ingenzi, zagize icyo zigeraho mu kwirinda ko habaho inzara ikomeye itewe n'ibura ry'ibiribwa yari itegerejwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani, aho umusaruro w'ibikomoka ku buhinzi n'ubworozi uri ku kigero cyo hejuru, nta kugabanuka gukomeye kwabayeho, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera, nk'uko byemezwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
Amashyiga y'ibiribwa yabonetse mu gihe gito, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa basesaga ibiryo by'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone indyo yuzuye.
Mu Butaliyani, hari itegeko nk'iryo risaba ababikora kubika ibicuruzwa by'ibiribwa mu gihe hazabaho imimerere nk'iyi.
Ku wa 16 Werurwe, itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ibiza bikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba za leta zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bwicuruzwa bwagabanutseho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari ihuriro ry'ubukungu n'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi cyafashwe nk'icyorezo gishobora guhungabanya ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu bw'igihugu, yavuze ko ibiciro bizakomeza kuba hejuru kugeza igihe tuzaba dufite ishusho igaragara y'uko ibintu bishobora kuzagenda.
Muri Mutarama 2020, abahanga bamwe batangaje ko ingaruka z'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ku iterambere ry'isi zishobora kurenga icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Abahanga bo muri Kaminuza ya Washington iri i St. Louis bagereranyije ko icyo cyorezo cyagize ingaruka ku isoko ku isi yose z'ibikoresho zigera kuri miriyari 300 z'amadolari y'Amerika, kandi ko gishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitumiza peteroli (OPEC) wavuze ko "bigaragambya" nyuma y'uko ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli byagabanutse cyane bitewe n'uko ubushake bw'u Bushinwa bwagabanutse.
Ku ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imari n'imigabane ku isi yose yagabanyutse bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo by'ibiciro by'amasoko yo muri Amerika, birimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500 Index, na Dow Jones Industrial Average, byanditse igihombo gikomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow yaguye amanota 1.191, igabanuka ry'umunsi umwe rikomeye cyane kuva mu bukene bw'imari mu 2007-2008.
Ibiciro by'amasoko y'ibiciro bya gatatu by'amasoko y'ubucuruzi byaguye ku kigero kirenga 10 ku ijana mu mpera z'icyumweru.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yongeye kwemeza igipimo cy'ububiko bwa leta y'Ubushinwa, ariko iharanira ko igaragaza ko nta ngaruka.
Ibiciro by'amasoko byongeye kumanuka bitewe no guhangayikishwa na coronavirus, igabanuka rikomeye ryabaye ku ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu bushobora kuzahara.
Umuhanga mu bukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba z'ibanze za banki nkuru na leta z'igihugu zagiyeho mu gihe.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu zagize icyo zitanga kurusha uko byari bimeze mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ryo mu 2008.
Ubukerarugendo ni kimwe mu by'inganda byahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye bitewe n'ingendo z'abakozi, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, n'ibikorwa bya leta byo kugabanya ingendo ku isi hose.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko, indege nyinshi zahagaritse ingendo kubera ko nta bantu benshi bari kuzifata, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe indege y'Ubwongereza yo mu karere ka Flybe yaguye.
Ingaruka byagize ku ngendo z'amato zari zigeze ku rugero rutari rugaragara mbere.
Hari n'amavuko n'ibibuga by'amagare by'i Burayi byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyibasiye igihugu cya Hong Kong mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru y'ubunani.
Ibirori by'abantu benshi byahagaritswe n'ubutegetsi bw'ibanze n'ibanze, harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka by'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa, kandi n'ibigo byigenga na byo byigaruriye amaduka n'ahantu nyaburanga, nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Benshi mu birori by'Ubunani n'ahantu hakunze guhagarikwa kugira ngo abantu batahurira hamwe, harimo n'Umujyi utagatifu wa Beijing hamwe n'ibirori byo mu nsengero gakondo.
Mu ntara 24 kuri 31 z'Ubushinwa, mu mijyi no mu turere, abayobozi bongereye iminsi mikuru y'ubunani kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare kandi bategeka ko aho bakorera hose batongera gufungura kugeza icyo gihe.
Ibice by'ibihugu by'iburasirazuba ni byo byinjiza 80% by'umusaruro mbumbe w'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa hanze.
Hong Kong yahagurukiye kurwanya indwara zandura ku rwego rwo hejuru kandi itangaza ko hari ibihe bidasanzwe, gufunga amashuri kugeza mu kwezi kwa gatatu, no guhagarika ibirori by'umwaka mushya.
Ibicuruzwa mu masoko yo mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo byagabanutseho 40 ku ijana.
Ibigo byo muri Amerika ya ruguru n'ibyo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati byaguye ku kigero cya 50-60%.
Ibi kandi byatumye habaho igabanuka rya 33-43% ryumuvuduko wamaguru ku masoko mu kwezi kwa Werurwe ugereranije no muri Gashyantare.
Abakora ibigo by'ubucuruzi ku isi bashyizeho ingamba zinyongera, zirimo kuzamura isuku, gushyiraho ibikoresho by'ubushyuhe kugirango bapime ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi, no guhagarika ibikorwa. Nk'uko bitangazwa na Komisiyo y'ubukungu y'umuryango w'abibumbye muri Amerika y'epfo, icyorezo cyatewe n'icyorezo gishobora gutuma abantu bari mu bukene bukabije muri Amerika y'Epfo biyongeraho abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na miliyoni 22 ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze hatariho icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, igihe iki cyorezo cyari cyakwiriye cyane mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi.
Benshi mu bakozi bo mu cyaro b'Abashinwa bagera kuri miriyoni 300 bari mu kazi mu ntara z'imbere mu gihugu cyangwa mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miriyoni 10 batakaje akazi kandi basaba leta kubashakira imfashanyo.
Nkuko bigaragazwa n'ingengo y'imari ya Banki ya Leta ya St. Louis, icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutuma imirimo miliyoni 47 izarangira muri Amerika kandi igipimo cy'ubushomeri gishobora kugera kuri 32%.
Mu gice cya kabiri cya Werurwe, abakozi miliyoni 4 b'Abafaransa basabye ko bahawe imfashanyo y'ubushomeri bw'igihe gito, naho abakozi miliyoni 1 b'Abongereza basabye inguzanyo y'inguzanyo rusange.
Imirimo y'ubucuruzi bw'igihe gito y'Abadage yarahawe inguzanyo n'Abafaransa n'Abongereza.
Hirya no hino ku isi, inganda z'ubuhanzi n'umurage ndangamuco byagizweho ingaruka zikomeye n'iki cyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango n'abantu ku giti cyabo, yaba abifitemo akazi cyangwa abiyitirira.
Amashyirahamwe y'umuco n'ubuhanzi yihatira gushimangira ubutumwa bwayo (benshi batanga inkunga y'amafaranga) yo gutanga umurage w'umuco ku baturage, kurinda abakozi bayo n'abaturage, no gushyigikira abahanzi igihe cyose bishoboka.
Muri Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose no mu byiciro bitandukanye, inzu ndangamurage, ububiko, ibibanza byerekana, n'ibindi bigo ndangamuco birafungwa igihe kitagira ingano, hamwe n'imurika, ibitaramo, ibitaramo byasibwe cyangwa byasubitswe.
Mu gusubiza, hashyizweho ingamba zikomeye zo gutanga serivisi z'ubundi buryo binyuze ku rubuga. Indi ngaruka mbi y'iyi ndwara iheruka kandi yihuta cyane ni uguhagarika ibikorwa by'idini, imikino ikomeye, n'ibindi bikorwa by'imibereho, nka muzika n'ibirori, amakoraniro y'ikoranabuhanga, n'imyambarire.
Nanone kandi, mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru ya Pasika, abantu benshi bagiye mu materaniro, bakareba uko abantu b'i Roma babona ibintu, bakumva ko ari ibintu bidasanzwe.
Amadini menshi ashishikariza abakristu bageze mu zabukuru kuguma mu rugo no kutitaba misa ku cyumweru; insengero zimwe na zimwe zitanga amasengesho y'itorero binyuze kuri radiyo, kuri interineti cyangwa kuri televiziyo, mu gihe izindi zitanga amasengesho yo mu modoka cyangwa kuri telefoni.
Mu gihe Kiliziya Gatolika ya Roma yari imaze gufunga insengero n'utubandi twazo no gufungura ikibuga cya Petero Mutagatifu, abandi bayobozi b'amadini na bo bahagaritse ibikorwa byabo no kugabanya umubare w'abantu bashoboraga guhurira mu nsengero, mu misigiti, mu masinagogi, mu nsengero no muri gurdwaras.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Iran yatangaje ko isengesho ryo ku wa Gatanu ryahagaritswe mu turere twazahajwe n'icyorezo n'ahantu ho gusengera nyuma hafungiwe, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga n'abaturage bayo kwinjira ahantu hera cyane i Mecca na Medina.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus cyatumye habaho ihungabana rikomeye cyane muri gahunda y'imikino ku isi kuva nyuma y'intambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Ibyinshi mu birori bikomeye bya siporo byakuweho cyangwa byasubitswe, harimo UEFA Champions League 2019-2020, Premier League 2019-2020, UEFA Euro 2020, NBA shampiyona 2019-2020, na NHL shampiyona 2019-2020.
Iki cyorezo cyahinduye gahunda ya Siporo yo mu mpeshyi 2020, yari iteganyijwe gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; Komite Olempike Mpuzamahanga yatangaje ku ya 24 Werurwe ko iki gikorwa "kizasubirwamo nyuma ya 2020, ariko ntikizaba nyuma y'impeshyi ya 2021". Ku isi hose, za kasinos n'ahandi hantu h'imikino byafunzwe kandi ibiganiro by'imikino ya poker byimitswe cyangwa byasibwe.
Ibi byatumye benshi mu bakina urusimbi bahindukirira imikino yo gukina urusimbi, imbuga nyinshi zo gukina urusimbi kuri interineti zivuga ko habayeho kwiyongera kwinshi kw'abashaka kwiyandikisha.
Amakinamico menshi akomeye nka Broadway nayo yasubitse igitaramo.
Abahanzi barimo gushakisha uburyo bwo gukomeza gukora no gusangiza ibikorwa byabo kuri interineti mu buryo bunyuranye n'ibikorwa bisanzwe, nko gutangiza ibitaramo binyuze kuri interineti cyangwa gukora "ibirori" bishingiye ku rubuga ku bahanzi kugira ngo bagaragaze, bakwirakwize kandi batangaze ibikorwa byabo.
Imyinshi muri meme za interineti zivuga kuri coronavirus zashyizwe ku rubuga, abantu benshi bahindukiraga ku myidagaduro no ku bintu biganisha ku myidagaduro mu gihe cy'amakuba.
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira, hagaragaye ubwiyongere bw'urwikekwe, urwango ruterwa n'abanyamahanga n'ivangura rishingiye ku moko ku bantu bakomoka mu Bushinwa no mu Burasirazuba bwa Aziya, ndetse n'abo mu duce twazahajwe n'icyorezo i Burayi, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika no mu bindi bihugu.
Ibikorwa by'ubwoba, urwikekwe n'urwango byagaragaye mu bihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika.
Raporo yo muri Gashyantare (igihe abenshi mu barwaye bari bakiri mu Bushinwa) yagaragaje imyumvire y'ivangura rya kiremwamuntu yagaragaye mu matsinda atandukanye ku isi yose ko Abashinwa bakwiriye kwakira virusi cyangwa bakemera ibyo bavuga ko ari ibihembo byabo.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byo muri Afurika na byo byagiye byibasira u Bushinwa.
Abaturage benshi bo muri Wuhan na Hubei batanze amakuru ko hari abantu bababazwa n'ivangura rishingiye ku moko yabo.
Hari ubufasha bwatanzwe ku Bashinwa, haba kuri interineti cyangwa ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, no ku bantu bo mu turere virusi yagezeho.
Nyuma yo gukwirakwiza icyorezo mu bihugu bishya, abantu bo mu Butaliyani, igihugu cya mbere mu Burayi cyibasiwe n'icyorezo gikomeye cya COVID-19, bashobora kuba n'ibanga ry'ikikekwa n'iterabwoba. Abaturage bo mu bihugu birimo Malaysia, Nouvelle Zelande, Singapore na Koreya y'Epfo babanje gusinya ku busabe bwo kubuza Abashinwa kwinjira mu bihugu byabo mu rwego rwo kugerageza gukumira indwara.
Mu Buyapani, amagambo akomeye nka #ChineseDontComeToJapan (Abashinwa ntibakwiriye kuza mu Buyapani) yatangiye gukoreshwa cyane kuri Twitter.
Abashinwa kimwe n'abandi bantu bo muri Aziya bo mu Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika batangaje ko habayeho ukwiyongera kw'ihohoterwa rishingiye ku moko no gukubitwa.
Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump, yanenzwe kuba yaragaragaje ko coronavirus ari "Virus yo mu Bushinwa", amagambo abenshi mu bamunenga bavuga ko ari amagambo y'ivangura kandi ko arwanya Ubushinwa.
Abigaragambyaga muri Ukraine bagabye igitero ku modoka za bisi zari zitwaye abanyekongo n'abanyamahanga bari bavuye i Wuhan bajya i Novi Sanzhary.
Abanyeshuri bo mu majyaruguru y'uburasirazuba bw'u Buhinde, ku mupaka w'u Bushinwa, biga mu mijyi minini y'u Buhinde, bavuga ko bahuye n'ibibazo by'ihohoterwa rishingiye ku cyorezo cya koronavirusi.
Perezida w'ishyaka rya Bharatiya Janata Party mu ntara ya West Bengal, Dilip Ghosh, yavuze ko u Bushinwa bwangije ibidukikije "niyo mpamvu Imana yabihoreye".
Iri tangazo ryamaganwe na konsula y'u Bushinwa i Kolkata, ivuga ko "byabayeho". Mu Bushinwa, urwango rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura ku baturage batari Abashinwa byatangiye kubera icyorezo, abanyamahanga bagaragazwa nk '"imyanda y'abanyamahanga" kandi bagashyirwa mu cyiciro cy '"imyanda".
Ibinyamakuru byinshi byatangaga amakuru kuri coronavirus byayikuyeho igice cyangwa byose.
