Igenzura rya laboratwari ku ndwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 rikubiyemo uburyo bwo gutahura ko virusi iriho ndetse no gutahura ko hari intumbi z'umubiri zikorerwa mu gusubiza ubwandu.
Kugira virusi mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kigeragezo kirasanzwe kandi cyakozwe mu rwego rwo gutahura virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 RNA gusa.
Ibi bipimo bikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyangwa bugikomeye.
Kubona antibodies (serology) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'amaraso byerekana umubare w'abantu bamaze kwandura, harimo n'abari bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batamenyekana cyangwa se nta na kimwe bagaragaje.
Ibipimo by'ukuri by'uburwayi bw'indwara n'ubwirinzi bw'ubwoko bw'abantu bishobora kumenyekana bivuye muri iki kizamini.
Kubera gupima bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bwandu bwa virusi mu baturage.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini by'abarenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rikomeye mu mibare y'ibizamini byakozwe n'ibihugu.
Ibi bitekerezo bishobora kugira ingaruka ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba iri hejuru cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Gukoresha uburyo bwo gupima hakoreshejwe ikinyabutabire cya "real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction" (rRT-PCR), ibi bizageragezwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo no gupima mu mazuru cyangwa mu mazuru.
Muri rusange, ibisubizo biboneka mu gihe cy'amasaha make kugeza ku minsi ibiri.
Ibizamini bya RT-PCR byakozwe ku isohoro ry'umugongo ni byo byonyine byiringirwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma, virusi ishobora gukira mu muhogo ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ubundi, ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibipimo bishobora gukusanywa bivuye mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bw'imbere hakoreshejwe kateteri yo mu kanwa cyangwa mu kwuka (igitsike).
Kimwe mu byiciro bya mbere by'igeragezwa rya PCR cyatangijwe i Charité, Berlin, muri Mutarama 2020 hifashishijwe uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga bwo gusubiramo mu gihe cya vuba bwa polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), maze hakorwa ibikoresho by'igeragezwa bigera ku 250,000 byo gukwirakwizwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwatangije igerageza kuri 23 Mutarama 2020.Ikigo cya Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech cyatangije icyuma cyo gupima SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Iyi mashini ishakisha gen "E" ikoreshwa na beta ya coronavirus zose, na gen RdRp yihariye kuri SARS-CoV-2.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu masosiyete ya mbere yahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa n'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe imiti mu Bushinwa mu buryo bw'ibanze bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bwo gupima hifashishijwe PCR. Muri Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatangije uburyo bushya bwo gupima virusi ya koronavirusi nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) mu buryo bw'igihe nyacyo (RT-PCR) mu mavuriro y'ubuzima rusange binyuze mu kigo mpuzamahanga gishinzwe iby'imiti.
Kimwe mu bipimo bitatu byagenewe mu bipimo by'ibikoresho by'ubwoko bwa kera byatanze ibisubizo bidashidikanywaho kubera ikosa ry'ibikoresho, kandi ibipimo by'ibizamini bya CDC muri Atlanta byari bigabanijwe; ibi byatumye mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020 ibipimo bigera ku 100 ku munsi bifatwa.
Igenzura rikoresha ibice bibiri byafashwe nk'aho ridashoboka kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, hanyuma gusa laboratwari z'igihugu na laboratwari z'ibanze zemerewe gukora ibizamini.
Iki cyorezo cyemejwe n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura ibiribwa n'imiti mu rwego rwo kwifashisha mu bihe bidasanzwe.
