Gukaraba intoki, byitwa kandi isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gusukura intoki z'umuntu ugamije gukuraho umwanda, amavuta, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune buri gihe mu "bihe bikomeye" by'umunsi bibuza ikwirakwizwa ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'iseru na kolera, zanduzwa mu nzira y'imyanda.
Nanone kandi, abantu bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa se ibicurane, iyo bakoresheje intoki zidahumanye mu gihe bagiye gukora ku maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga mu mara).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi ari na byo by'ingenzi cyane mu gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni ibi: mbere na nyuma yo kuvoma, nyuma yo koza umwana cyangwa guhindura imyenda, mbere yo kumwonsa, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gutunganya inyama, ifi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu gihe nta mazi n'isabune bihari, intoki zishobora gukaraba hakoreshejwe ivu.
Mbere yo gutegura amafunguro, mu gihe utegura ndetse na nyuma yo gutegura.
Mbere na nyuma yo gufasha abarwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura inkweto cyangwa gukaraba umwana umaze gukoresha ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhanagura izuru, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Iyo umuntu akoze ku matungo, ku biribwa by'amatungo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'intoki mu buvuzi yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bijyanye n'ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwivuza bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki ni ugukura intoki ku ndwara (bakiteri, virusi, cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho byangiza cyangwa byanduza.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane cyane ku bantu bakora mu byo kurya cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko kandi ni ingirakamaro ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite inyungu nyinshi z'ubuzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya grippe, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo; kwirinda indwara z'ibyorezo z'impiswi; kugabanya indwara z'ubuhumekero;
Kandi byagabanyije impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2013 bwerekanye ko kongera imikoreshereze y'isuku y'intoki bishobora kugabanya cyane uburebure bw'abana bato.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, impfu z'abana bahitanwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero ndetse n'isukari zishobora kugabanuka hatangijwe ihinduka ryoroheje mu myitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Icyo gikorwa cyoroshye gishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa n'umubare w'abahitanwa na yo hafi 50%.
Gukurikiza uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki byagabanya umubare w'abandura indwara zo mu maraso ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu; ibyo bikaba bigerwaho binyuze mu gutanga amazi meza mu turere tw'abaturage batishoboye.
48% by'igabanuka ry'umubare w'abafite diyabete rishobora kwerekezwa ku gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwonyine bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda diyabete n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ISPA), nk'imyitwarire yo mu mutwe ikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri, no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Pneumonia, ari nayo mpamvu nyamukuru ya ISPA, niyo ndwara ya mbere ihitana abana bato; iyi ndwara ihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Iseru n'indwara z'ibyorezo by'ibicurane, bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni eshatu n'igice buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero nk'umuco umuntu agomba gukurikiza, bishobora kurokora ubuzima bwinshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubundi buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwivuza, kandi bikagabanya urupfu rw'ubuhumekero hafi kimwe cya kabiri n'urupfu rw'indwara z'ubuhumekero ku kigero cya kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki bikunze guhuzwa n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'igice cya gahunda y'amazi, isuku n'isukura (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda indwara y'ibicurane yandurira mu buryo butaziguye.
Ingaruka nke yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu bitewe no kuruha kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012 muri Danemark bwasanze gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera ikibazo cy'uruhu rubabaza kandi rukanuka, bizwi nka eczema cyangwa dermatitis yo mu biganza, bikunda kugaragara cyane mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo bibonwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'igwingira.
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwizwa ry'indwara mu kanwa no mu kibuno, ari byo: mbere na nyuma yo gukoresha umusaruro (isuku, gusohora cyane), nyuma yo gusukura umwana (gusimbuza inkweto), mbere yo guha umwana icyo kunywa, mbere yo kurya na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa guteka inyama, ifi, cyangwa inkoko.
Indi mpamvu y'ingenzi yo gukaraba intoki neza kugira ngo wirinde kwandura indwara, ni mbere na nyuma yo gukemura ibikomere; nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora, cyangwa guhumura mu mazuru; nyuma yo gukora ku mwanda w'inyamaswa cyangwa gukorana n'inyamaswa; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, igipimo cyo gukaraba intoki n'isabune kiracyari hasi.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwerekanye ko ku kigereranyo cya 38.7% by'ingo zikoresha umwotsi mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwerekanye ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo kiri hejuru kuri 97 ku ijana; Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziri hagati na 77 ku ijana; n'Ubushinwa ku gipimo kiri hasi kuri 23 ku ijana.
Porogaramu yo kwita ku buzima bw'ibanze yashyizweho mu rwego rw'uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byo gufasha ubuzima bw'abana n'uburezi.
Gupfusha ibiheri kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune no gukaraba amenyo buri munsi ukoresheje fluoride, ni byo by'ibanze muri iyo gahunda y'igihugu.
Iyo gahunda yageze ku bintu byiza na Indoneziya.
Gukaraba umubiri bikomeza kwiyongera iyo ukoresheje isabune cyangwa umuti wiyuhagira.
Impamvu ya mbere ya sabune n'isuku ni ukugabanya inzitizi ku kintu kiva mu mazi kandi bigatuma kirushaho kumeneka.
Amazi yonyine ni umuti wo gukaraba uruhu udafite ubushobozi kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bigize imyanda ikorwamo, bidashobora kumuka mu mazi.
Icyakora, amazi menshi ni yo afasha mu gusukura ibinure n'indemamubiri.
Imyenda y'isabune, kubera ko ishobora gukoreshwa kenshi, ishobora kuba irimo mikorobe zavuye mu mikoreshereze ya mbere.
Ubushakashatsi buciriritse bwibanda ku kwimurwa kwa mikorobe mu isabune yanduye, bwasanze nta kwimurwa gushoboka kubera ko mikorobe yahumanyijwe n'umwimerere.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara za SIDA cyavuze ko "sabune y'amazi ikurwamo n'umuntu itagakozeho intoki ari yo nziza".
Isabune za bakeri zirashishikarizwa cyane mu baturage bafite ubuzima bwiza.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya yigeze igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti y'umuti w'isuku cyangwa umuti wica udukoko ari byiza ku binyabuzima byirinda imiti ya antibiyotike mu bidukikije.
Ariko, isabune zirimo imiti isanzwe ya bakteria nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rurerure rw'ibinyabuzima byayigometseho.
Nubwo rero ubwo bwoko bw'isupu bufite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe, bushobora kuba butari bufite ubushobozi nk'ubwo buvugwa.
Usibye kuba ari surfactant na protection substances z'uruhu, formulations zigezweho zishobora kuba zirimo acides (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) nka pH regulator, acide benzoate nka antimicrobial active, na conditioner y'uruhu ikomeza (mucanga wa crocodile, vitamine, menthol, extract z'ibimera). Isesengura ryimbitse ryakozwe na Kaminuza ya Kaminuza ya Oregon Ishami ry'ubuzima rusange ryerekana ko isabune isanzwe ari ingirakamaro kimwe na sabune yo kurwanya mikoro yo mu rwego rw'abakiriya irimo triclosan mu gukumira indwara no kuvanaho mikorobe mu biganza.
Amazi ashyushye umuntu yakoresha mu gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ku buryo yakwica mikorobe.
Bakteriya ikura vuba cyane mu gihe umubiri uri ku kigero cy'ubushyuhe bwa dogere 37 z'igice cya Selisiyusi.
Amazi ashyushye kandi yuzuye isabune agira ingaruka nziza cyane kurusha amazi akonje y'isabune mu gukuraho amavuta y'ibanze arinda ibyonnyi n'uduheri.
Ariko kandi, binyuranye n'ibyo abantu benshi bizera, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu bya siyansi bwerekanye ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta cyo bihindura ku mikorobe ziba mu ntoki.
Umuti uvura ibiganza cyangwa umuti wica udukoko ni umuti w'isuku utari uwa water.
Mu mpera za 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo guhanagura intoki idafite amazi (yitwa kandi alcohol-based hand rubbers, antiseptic hand rubbers, cyangwa hand sanitizers) yatangiye kumenyekana.
Benshi muri ibi bikoresho by'isuku bishingiye kuri isopropyl alcohol cyangwa etanol, byakozwe hamwe n'ibikoresho bikoroshya nka Carbomer (polymeri ya acrylic acid) mu buryo bwa gels cyangwa hamwe na humektan nka glycerine muburyo bworoshye cyangwa busa kugirango bikoreshwe kandi bigabanya ingaruka zo kumuka kwa alcohol.
Kwongeraho hydrogen peroxide yoroheje byongera ibikorwa bya antimicrobial. Kwisiga intoki bifite byibuze 60-95% by'inzoga ni umuti mwiza wica mikorobe.
Kunywa inzoga zikoreshwa mu gusya, bica udukoko dutera indwara, udukoko dutera indwara nyinshi (MRSA na VRE), udukoko dutera indwara y'igituntu, udukoko tw'ibyorezo twinshi (hakubiyemo HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, influenza na hepatite), n'udukoko tw'ibyorezo.
Kunywa inzoga z'ubuyobe zigizwe na 70% bya alcohol zikiza 99,97% (igabanuka rya log 3,5, rifite agaciro kangana na 35 decibel) z'udukoko tw'amaboko nyuma y'amasegonda 30 nyuma yo gukoreshwa, kandi 99,99% kugeza 99,999% (igabanuka rya log 4 kugeza 5) z'udukoko tw'amaboko nyuma y'iminota 1 nyuma yo gukoreshwa.
Ibinini by'intoki bikoresha inzoga ntibikora ku bwoko bwa norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), intandaro y'indwara y'umwijima.
Imbere n'inyuma by'ibiganza byombi ndetse no ku nkokora n'impande z'intoki zose, bihanagurwa mu masegonda 30 kugeza ubwo amazi, umukoba cyangwa gel byuma.
Ikigo cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara muri Amerika cyatanze inama yo gukaraba intoki aho gukaraba intoki, cyane cyane iyo intoki zisa nabi.
Gukoresha cyane imiti yica mikorobe byatewe n'uko ikoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye kandi ikagira imikorere yica vuba; ariko, imiti yica mikorobe ntiyagombye gukoreshwa mu gusimbura gukaraba intoki, keretse iyo isabune n'amazi bidahari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikozwe muri alcohol bishobora gutuma uruhu rukomera, keretse niba emolien na/cyangwa umusemburo w'uruhu wongeyeho formula.
Ingaruka z'amazi y'inzoga zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa se zikurwaho hifashishijwe inyongera ya glycerine na/cyangwa izindi emolien mu mabwiriza.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, gukanda intoki hakoreshejwe inzoga zirimo emolien byateye uruhu gukara no gukonja cyane ugereranyije n'isabune n'imiti yica mikorobe.
Indwara y'umwijima, urticaria, cyangwa se guhorana ibishishwa by'inzoga cyangwa ibindi bikoresho byo mu bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki, ni ibintu bidakunze kubaho.
Kuba umuntu afite ubumuga bwo kutumva butuma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo guhura n'abantu batamureba, ni byo bituma abahanga muri ibyo bintu bavuga ko gukaraba intoki ari byiza kuruta gukaraba amazi n'isabune.
Nubwo ari ingirakamaro, imiti itari iy'amazi ntiyeza intoki ku binyabuzima, ahubwo irazirwanya.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, imiti yo gukaraba intoki ntabwo igira ingaruka nziza nk'isabune n'amazi mu kurinda ikwirakwira rya virusi nyinshi zandura bitewe n'uko zikiri mu biganza.
Ibyiza bya cyanide mu gukaraba intoki bitagendanye n'inzoga biterwa cyane n'ibikoresho n'uburyo byakozwe, kandi mu mateka y'ibicuruzwa byakoze nabi cyane kurusha inzoga n'imiti yo gukaraba.
Vuba aha, uburyo bwo gukoresha benzalkonium chloride bwerekanye ko bufite ibikorwa bya antimicrobial bidasiba kandi byongera nyuma yo gukoresha, bitandukanye na alcohol, ubuhanga bwayo bwerekanwe ko bumanuka nyuma yo gukoresha kenshi, birashoboka ko bitewe no kwiyongera kw'ibyago.
Abantu benshi bo mu miryango ikennye ntibashobora kubona isabune, bityo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ubutaka mu cyimbo cyayo.
Umukungugu cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kuba ingirakamaro kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko nta cyo bivuze nko gukoresha isabune.
Kimwe mu bintu bihangayikishije ni uko mu gihe ubutaka cyangwa ivu byaba byanduye mikorobe, bishobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira aho kugabanya ubukana bwayo.
Kimwe na sabune, umukungugu ni umuti wica udukoko kuko, iyo uhuye n'amazi, umukungugu ugize umuti w'ibinure.
OMS isaba ko habaho ivu n'umusenyi nk'ibindi bikoresho by'isabune mu gihe isabune itariho.
Gukaraba intoki neza nk'uko byashyizweho n'Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, mu kwirinda ikwirakwizwa ry'indwara harimo:
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Bagomba gukoresha amazi meza kuko basanze amazi arimo uburozi ashobora kuba yanduye, ariko ubushyuhe bw'amazi bwo nta cyo buvuze.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, harimo n'inyuma z'intoki, mu nkokora no munsi y'amano.
Isabune ikura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune kurusha amazi yonyine.
Gukubita urushyi mu masegonda 20.
Gupfukura bituma habaho guhanagura, bigatuma udukoko twinshi twanduza twinjira mu mubiri, kandi iyo umuntu akomeje gukaraba, bituma udukoko twinshi twandujwe.
Yicaye hasi, mu mazi ashyushye.
Gukaraba mu gikombe bishobora gutuma intoki zongera kwandura.
Ujye ukaraba mu gitambaro cyangwa se ureke bihumuke.
Ibice bikunze kurengaho ni ibiganza, inzara, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'amano.
Ibishishwa by'imashini n'amabara y'ipiki bishobora kubamo mikorobe.
Ubusanzwe, amavuta y'amazi arinda intoki gukama; uruhu rwumye rushobora kwangiza uruhu, bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura.
Amahitamo menshi y'igiciro gito arashobora gukorwa kugirango yorohereze gukaraba intoki mugihe amazi ya robine na/cyangwa isabune bitagishoboka, urugero, kuvoma amazi ya sherry cyangwa icupa ryahambiriwe kandi ryashushanyije kandi/cyangwa gukoresha ivu, iyo bibaye ngombwa, mubihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu bihe aho amazi acungwa (nk'amashuri cyangwa uduce tw'icyaro mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hariho ibisubizo bikoresha amazi, nka "tippy-tap", kimwe n'ibindi byiciro by'igiciro gito.
Ikoranabuhanga ryoroshye cyane ni ijerekani y'amazi ikoresheje ijerekani y'amazi ihamye, ijerekani ikoreshwa n'amaguru kugira ngo amazi agere mu biganza, n'isabune.
Gusuzuma intoki neza ni igice cy'ingenzi mu isuku y'intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo gusukura intoki mu bwiherero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bwerekana ko impapuro zikoreshwa mu gupima intoki zimeze neza cyane kurusha izipfunyika intoki zikoreshwa mu kubaga.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, i Londres, bwatewe inkunga n'uruganda rw'impu, European Tissue Symposium, hagamijwe kugereranya igipimo cy'isuku y'impu, ibipfunyika intoki bishyushye n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rwa jet.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumisha intoki ukoresheje akuma gashyuha, imibare yose y'utunyabuzima yagaragaye yiyongeraho 194% ku bipfunsi by'intoki n'254% ku kiganza.
Kumisha mu kirere byongera ingano ya za bagiteri ku kigereranyo cya 42% ku mpyiko z'intoki na 15% ku biganza.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki ukoresheje impapuro, umubare w'udukoko ku kigero kiri hagati ya 76% mu ntoki na 77% ku biganza. Abahanga kandi bakoze igerageza kugira ngo hamenyekane ibyago byo kwandura ku bandi bantu n'aho hantu hakoreshejwe ubwiherero bitewe n'uburyo bwo kumesa.
Umwuka usukura umwuka wa jet, usohora umwuka uva mu cyumba ku muvuduko w'amaguru wa 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), ushobora guhumeka udukoko duto duto mu biganza no mu cyumba kandi ushobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero ndetse n'ahantu hari ubwiherero ku metero 2.
Gukoresha igikoma cy'umwuka ushyushye byongera mikorobe mu metero 0.25 uvuye ku gikoma.
Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, uburyo butandukanye bwo kumisha intoki bwahishuwe.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, hagaragaye impinduka zikurikira mu mikorobe:
Hariho ibintu byinshi by'imashini zikora ibintu byo guhanagura intoki, kandi ibyo bikoresho byagereranyijwe n'imashini zikora ibintu byo guhanagura intoki zikoresheje impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imyenda isukura intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukaraba mu gihe cy'urugendo mu gihe nta sabune n'amazi bihari.
Umuti wica udukoko dukoreshwa mu ntoki ugomba kuba urimo nibura 60% by'inzoga.
Gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi byatangiye gushyirwa mu bikorwa nyuma y'uko umuhanga mu bya fiziki w'Umunyahongiriya Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye akamaro kabyo (mu 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bitanga amakuru yibutsa abakozi bo mu bitaro gukaraba intoki mu gihe baba babyibagiwe.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abandura indwara ugabanuka bitewe no gukoresha ibyo bikoresho.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi bikorwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda 15, hakoreshejwe isabune n'amazi menshi cyangwa gel yo gukaraba no gukaraba buri gice cy'intoki.
Ibiganza bigomba guhanagurwa hamwe, intoki zikagendana.
Niba hari ibishishwa munsi y'amatama, ikimwaro cy'ubwoya gishobora gukoreshwa mu kubikuraho.
Kubera ko mikorobi zishobora kwibamo mu mazi, ni ngombwa ko ukaraba intoki neza kandi ukazigezaho impapuro zanduye.
Iyo umugozi umaze gukama, ukoreshwa mu gufunga ibyuma by'amazi (kandi iyo bibaye ngombwa ukoresha inzira yo gusohoka).
Ibyo bituma amaboko y'abo bantu adashobora kwandura.
Mu rwego rwo kwita ku buzima, gukaraba intoki bigamije gukuraho mikorobe ziterwa n'indwara (mikorobe) no kwirinda kuzikwirakwiza.
Ikinyamakuru The New England Journal of Medicine cyatangaje ko kubura gukaraba intoki bikiri ku rwego rutemewe mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, aho umubare munini w'abaganga n'abaforomo bakomeje kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku murwayi bityo bakanduza mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya ubwandu bw'amaraso bufitanye isano n'ibihaha ku kigero cya 66%. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima ryasohoye urupapuro rugaragaza uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki no gukaraba intoki mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Amabwiriza agenga isuku y'intoki ya OMS ashobora no kuboneka ku rubuga rwayo kugira ngo abantu bayisobanure.
Isesengura rifite aho rihuriye ryakozwe na Whitby et al.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'amaboko mu gihe bigomba kugaragaza ko amategeko yubahirizwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) rifite "Ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
Nyuma yo kwanduzwa n'amaraso/isukari yo mu mubiri
mbere yo gukora isuku,
Nyuma yo kuvura umurwayi, kongeraho imiti yica udukoko mu isuku (sabune "imiti" cyangwa "anti-microbial") bikora nk'ibikoresho by'isuku.
Kubwibyo, kureka kubura intoki mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa mugihe ingirabuzimafatizo zifite ubudahangarwa bwa antibiyotike. Kugirango 'gukaraba' intoki mbere y'ubuvuzi, bikenera robine ishobora gucana no guhagarika udakora, chlorhexidin cyangwa iodine, isuka yanduye yo kumisha intoki nyuma yo gukaraba, n'iburashi isukuye yo gukaraba hamwe nibindi bikoresho byanduye byo gusukura munsi y'imisumari.
Ibishushanyo byose bigomba gukurwaho.
Iyi nzira isaba ko umuntu akaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, ubusanzwe iminota 26.
Igihe kirekire cyo gukaraba (iminota 10) ntabwo gikenewe.
Mu gihe umuntu arimo akaraba, amazi ari mu kiganza cy'iburyo agomba kurindwa gusubira mu kiganza.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, bazikamisha igitambaro cy'umweru maze bambare umwenda w'umutimanama.
Kugira ngo wirinde ikwirakwizwa ry'indwara, ni byiza gukaraba intoki cyangwa gukoresha umuti wica udukoko mbere na nyuma yo gukorana n'umuntu urwaye.
Ku bijyanye no kugenzura indwara ya staphylococcus mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu nini yo gukaraba intoki ituruka kuri 20% bya mbere byo gukaraba, kandi ko inyungu y'inyongera iboneka gake cyane iyo inshuro yo gukaraba intoki yongerewe hejuru ya 35%.
Gukoresha isabune isanzwe bitera indwara zanduza inshuro eshatu mu kwandura indwara zanduza ibiribwa ugereranyije no gukoresha isabune irwanya mikorobe. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti urimo alcohol no gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune irwanya mikorobe n'igihe cy'amasegonda 30 kuri buri kimwe cyose bigaragaza ko gukaraba intoki ukoresheje alcohol bigabanya kwanduzwa na mikorobe ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune irwanya mikorobe.
Ariko, isabune n'amazi biruta cyane igishishwa cy'intoki cy'alcool mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 y'indwara y'ibicurane A na Clostridium difficile ku biganza. Gahunda zo guteza imbere isuku y'intoki mu bigo by'ubuzima zishobora kuba zigizwe n'uburezi ku bakozi ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki, kongera igishishwa cy'intoki cy'alcool, no kuburira abakozi mu magambo no mu nyandiko.
Hakenewe ubundi bushakashatsi kugira ngo hamenyekane uburyo bwiza bwo kuvura mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune byemezwa nk'uburyo bw'ibanze kandi buhendutse bwo kugera ku buzima bwiza ndetse no kurya neza.
Ariko, kubura amazi yizewe, isabune, cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abaturage, amashuri n'ahantu h'akazi bituma intego yo kugera ku ngeso yo gukaraba intoki ku isi yose iba ikibazo.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, amazi yo gukaraba hafi y'ubwiherero bwite cyangwa ubwogero rusange ntakunze kuboneka, nubwo uburyo bwo gukora ahantu ho gukaraba byoroheje buhari.
Ariko kandi, kuba abantu badafata intoki neza bishobora guterwa n'akamenyero kabi, aho guterwa no kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Gushishikariza no gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku ngingo z'amabwiriza, kongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki, no guhindura imyitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo bigire ingaruka nziza, hagomba gukorwa igenzura no gusuzuma.
Ubushakashatsi bugenzuwe ku masomo 70 bwerekanye ko uburyo bw'abaturage bugira ingaruka nziza mu kuzamura isuku y'intoki muri LMIC, mu gihe gahunda yo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga itari ingirakamaro.
Iyo ibisabwa by'inyongera byujuje, ishuri rishobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe rigasubira ku yindi, amaherezo rikajya ku yindi y'inyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki bikorwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya uburwayi n'impfu z'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo kumenyekanisha intego yo guhindura imyitwarire.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bijyanye n'igiciro cyo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, mu rwego rwo kwirinda uburwayi, cyangwa mu rwego rwo gupima imyaka umuntu amara arwaye.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bugaragaza ko gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune ari byo by'ingenzi cyane mu gutuma amafaranga atagera ku bikorwa by'amazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu, cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere y'ubutabazi, nk'umubyeyi wabyaye cyangwa umusirikare wakomeretse mu bitaro, bwa mbere bwamenywe mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abahanga babiri mu buvuzi bw'intoki: Ignaz Semmelweis w'umuganga w'Umunyahongiriya wakoraga i Vienna, mu Budage, na Florence Nightingale, "uwashinze ubuvuzi bwa none" mu Bwongereza.
Icyo gihe, abantu benshi bari bakirizera ko indwara y'ibicurane yatewe n'umuvumba w'umuyaga.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo byandujwe n'ibiribwa n'ubwandu bw'indwara mu kwivuza byatumye Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, cyashishikariza abantu gukoresha isuku y'amaboko nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwizwa ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cya virusi ya H1N1 mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye ibihugu byinshi byibutsa akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda iyi ndwara.
Urugero, inyandiko "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki" zashyizwe iruhande rw'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu bwiherero rusange no mu bwiherero bw'amazu y'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege mu Budage.
Ijambo "gukaraba intoki" ryerekeza ku muntu utinya kugira icyo akora cyangwa ngo abe ari we wikorera.
Iri jambo rikomoka muri Bibiliya mu gitabo cya Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yakarabye intoki ku cyemezo cyo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko ryabaye ijambo rikoreshwa cyane mu muryango w'Abongereza.
Muri Macbeth, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ze buri gihe kugira ngo yeze ibishushanyo; igikorwa kigaragaza ko yicuza ibyaha yakoze ndetse n'ibyo yashoboye gushuka umugabo we ngo abikore.
Byongeye kandi, byaragaragaye ko nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa by'ubuhemu, abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi bakunze guha agaciro ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Ikindi kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gusabiriza baba bafite amahirwe make yo kugira uruhare mu bikorwa byo "gukorora" nk'ibikorwa by'ingurane, nko kwifatanya mu bikorwa by'ubwitange.
Kwiyuhagira kw'amaboko, gukoreshwa n'amazi, ariko nta sabune yo gukaraba intoki, ni igice cy'umugenzo wo gukaraba intoki mu madini menshi, harimo Ukwemera kwa Bahá'í, Abahindu, tevvilah na netilat yadayim muri Kiyahudi, Lavabo mu Bukristo, na Wudhu muri Islamu.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu, bose basabwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha imuhira.
Uretse n'ibyo, idini ry'Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasiki, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu, na ryo risaba abantu gukaraba intoki mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kurya.
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi bya COVID-19
Gukora ibikorwa by'ubuziranenge mu kwirinda COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo kwirinda no kwirinda mu kazi bugamije kwirinda icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19).
Gukora igenzura ry'ibyago ku kazi bihuje n'aho ukorera n'akazi ukora, bishingiye ku gusuzuma ibyago byo kwandura, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago ku bakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima ku kazi (OSHA), akazi k'ibyago byo kwandura bike cyane ni akazi gakorana n'abantu benshi n'abandi bakozi; muri ako kazi, hashishikarizwa ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe bari kwa muganga, kugira umuco wo guhumeka, no gukora isuku no guhanagura udukoko dukorera ahantu.
Imirimo ishobora gutuma umuntu ahura n'indwara harimo imirimo isaba guhura kenshi n'umuntu utazwi cyangwa ushobora kuba afite COVID-19, ariko ashobora kuba yaranduye bitewe n'uko hari ubwandu mu bantu cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Iri tsinda ryerekeza ku bakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, mu kazi ahantu hari umubare munini w'abaturage, no mu maduka acuruza ibintu byinshi.
Gukora ku buryo bw'ibanze bwo kwirinda iyi ndwara muri iki cyiciro, harimo gukoresha imashini z'umwuka z'ubuziranenge, gukingirwa guhumeka, no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu igihe ahuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu bigo nderabuzima n'iby'imva bagaragaweho n'abantu bazwiho cyangwa bikekwaho ko banduye COVID-19 bafite ibyago byo kwandura cyane, bikazamuka bikajya ku rwego rwo hejuru cyane mu gihe bakora ibikorwa byo gukwirakwiza isupu ku bantu bazwiho cyangwa bikekwaho ko banduye COVID-19, cyangwa bagafata cyangwa bagakora ku bipimo by'abantu bazwiho cyangwa bikekwaho kuba banduye COVID-19.
Ibi byangombwa by'abakozi birimo ibijyanye n'ubumenyi bw'ubuvuzi, urugero nk'iby'ibyumba by'umwuka bibi, n'iby'ubwirinzi bukwiriye akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka ku kazi.
Umukozi ashobora kudakora kubera ko arwaye, akeneye kwita ku bandi, cyangwa se kubera gutinya ko ashobora kuba yakwandurizwa.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka haba mu birebana n'ubwoko bw'ibicuruzwa bisabwa ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubikura (urugero nko guhaha mu gihe cy'akazi, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu modoka, cyangwa ku murongo).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu turere twoherejwemo COVID-19 bishobora guhungabana.
Gahunda ifata ingamba z'ibyago bijyanye n'ahantu henshi h'akazi n'imirimo y'akazi, harimo isoko y'ibyago, ibyago bituruka ku mutekano w'urugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago ku mukozi ku giti cye, nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Gahunda kandi igaragaza ingamba zikenewe zo guhangana n'izo ngaruka ndetse n'uburyo bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'icyorezo.
Gahunda zo kwitegura no kurwanya indwara zandura zishobora gukurikizwa hakurikijwe inama z'igihugu cyangwa iz'akarere.
Intego zo kurwanya icyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'ibyorezo, kubungabunga ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi sosiyete ziri mu bucuruzi.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ikigo gikora, bugira uruhare ku ngamba zo kuyirwanya.
Urwego rwo kugenzura ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu bijyanye n'umutekano w'akazi no kubungabunga ubuzima bw'abakozi mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago bishingiye ku bushobozi.
Iyo nta bushobozi bwo guhashya COVID-19 buhari, uburyo bwo guhangana burushaho kuba ingirakamaro ni uguhagarika ibikorwa by'ikoranabuhanga, hagakurikiraho ibikorwa by'ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakakurikiraho gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Gucunga by'umwihariko birimo gukingira abakozi ibyago bijyanye n'akazi bitagendeye ku myitwarire y'abakozi kandi bishobora kuba umuti uhenze cyane.
Gucunga by'akazi ni impinduka mu mategeko y'akazi cyangwa mu buryo bw'akazi bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho byo kwirinda (APD) bifatwa nk'ibifite ingaruka nke ugereranyije n'uburyo bwo kugenzura no kugenzura, ariko bishobora gufasha kwirinda bimwe mu byo umuntu yerekwa.
Ubwoko bwose bwa APD bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga kabamo ku mukozi, gushyirwaho neza uko bikwiye (urugero, respirator), kwambara neza kandi buri gihe, gusuzumwa, kwitabwaho no gusimbuzwa igihe cyose bibaye ngombwa, no gukurwa, gukosorwa no kubikwa neza cyangwa kujugunywa kugira ngo umuntu atagwa mu kirere.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima bwo mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gashyirwamo ibyago byo guhura n'ingaruka nke cyane ni ako umuntu akora mu buryo budahuza n'abantu benshi n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zigomba gukurikizwa mu byiciro byose by'akazi harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amahame y'ubuvuzi harimo guhisha gukorora no gusohora, gutanga imyanda no gushyiraho imyanda, gutegura akazi hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa kure cyangwa guhinduranya imirimo mu gihe cyo kuza no kuva, niba ari ngombwa, kubwira abakozi kudakoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gusukura no gutwika ahantu bakorera buri gihe.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwanduza byihuse ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abasura aho bakorera n'abandi bantu aho bakorera.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura no kwirinda indwara (CDC) giteganya ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara z'ubuhumekero bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba barangije kugira umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro, n'ibindi bimenyetso by'ubu burwayi mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 nta miti y'umuriro cyangwa indi miti ivura ibimenyetso, kandi ko politiki y'ikiruhuko cy'uburwayi igomba kuba yoroheje kugira ngo abakozi bashobore kuguma mu rugo kwita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi ko abakozi bagomba kumenya iyi politiki.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na OSHA, akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byo kwandura karimo akazi gasaba guhura hafi cyangwa kenshi muri metero 1,8 n'umuntu utazi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19, ariko ashobora kuba yanduye SARS-CoV-2 kubera ko yandura mu baturage bari hafi y'aho akorera, cyangwa kubera ko umuntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga akajya ahantu hakwirakwijwe COVID-19.
Iri tsinda ririmo abakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu h'akazi hafite abaturage benshi, no mu buryo bwo kugurisha buhambaye. Gukora ubuhanga bw'ubuhanga kuri iri tsinda no mu itsinda ryibangamiye cyane harimo gushyira filtere y'umwuka ikora neza, kongera ingano y'umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nka plastike y'indorerwamo yo gukingira, no gushyiraho amadirishya yo gutwara cyangwa imiterere y'abakozi. Gukora ubuyobozi kuri iri tsinda no mu itsinda ryibangamirwa cyane harimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza inama amaso ku maso na itumanaho ry'ibanze, gukora gahunda y'akazi ku gihe cyo kugera / kuza, guhagarika ingendo zidakenewe ahantu habaho COVID-19, guteza imbere gahunda yo gutumanaho byihutirwa harimo inama yo gusubiza impungenge z'abakozi, guha abakozi ubumenyi n'imyito ku bijyanye n'ibyago bya COVID-19 n'imyitwarire, gutoza abakozi gukoresha imyenda n'ibikoresho birinda bikingira imikorerwaho uburyo bwo kuyikoresha, gushyiraho ibikoresho by'ibanze by'akazi no gushyigikira ibikorwa by'abakozi birimo ubuziranenge kandi bisaba ko abantu bakoresha isuku buri gihe, gukumira abagenzi n'abakozi n'abandi, kw'abakozi no gukorana, nibura kwambara udupfukamunwa, cyangwa gukoresha udukingisho, cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'amaso, cyangwa kwirinda COVID-19 hamwe n'ibikingizi, cyangwa gukingira mu kazi, cyangwa kwirinda, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa kwirinda, cyangwa kwirinda, cyangwa gukoresha udukwirinda, cyangwa ku maso, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa guhangana n'ibishushobora gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, cyangwa gukingira, ku kazi, cyangwa ku bikenewe, cyangwa, cyangwa, cyangwa bikurinda, cyangwa, mu buryo, cyangwa, cyangwa mu gihe, mu, mu bikorwa, mu buryo, cyangwa, cyangwa, aho, mu, muburyo, cyangwa, mu, mu, mu, mu, mu, mu, mu, mu, mu, mu
Abakozi bo muri ibyo byiciro by'ubudahangarwa ntibakenera imashini z'ubuhumekero.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, mu mabwiriza yo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bagenzi harimo gutandukanya umurwayi n'abandi bantu bakamufata intera y'ibirometero 6, guha umukozi wo mu ndege kwita ku murwayi, no guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumuhisha umunwa n'amazuru mu gihe akoroye cyangwa anutse.
Abagenzi bagomba kwambara imyenda y'abaganga igihe bafashe umurwayi cyangwa bagakora ku mazi y'umubiri cyangwa ahantu hashobora kuba haranduye, ndetse n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu mu gihe umurwayi afite umuriro, gukorora cyane cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Uturindantoki n'ibindi bikoresho by'itumanaho bigomba kujugunywa mu isakoshi y'ibinyabuzima, kandi ubuso bwanduye bugomba gukosorwa no kwanduzwa nyuma. Ku ngendo z'ubucuruzi, harimo ubwato butwara abagenzi n'ubundi bwato butwara abagenzi, kwirinda kubangamira ubwato birimo gusubika urugendo mu gihe urwaye, kwigunga, no kumenyesha ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cy'ubwato ako kanya niba umuntu afite umuriro cyangwa indi myirondoro igihe ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, gukurikirana kwa muganga bikorerwa mu byumba by'abantu biherereye. Nubwo hashobora kuba hari ikwirakwizwa mu baturage, ku mashuri n'ibigo by'abana, CDC igaragaza ko hakwiye gufunga by'igihe gito kugira ngo hatagira umuntu wanduye cyangwa wanduza mu gihe yaba ari ku ishuri.
Mu gihe hari ubwandu mu baturage ku kigero cyo hasi cyangwa ku rugero ruciriritse, ingamba zo gukumira abantu zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa, zirimo: gusiba gusura ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, guteranira hamwe n'indi miryango, urugero nko kwiga siporo, kwiga muri korari cyangwa kurya muri cafeteria, kongera intera hagati y'ameza, igihe cyo kuza no kuvaho gikomeza, kugabanya abashyitsi batari ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho gukorera mu biro by'ubuzima ku bana bafite ibimenyetso nk'iby'ibicurane.
Niba hari ubwandu bukabije mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda kwegerana, kongera igihe cyo gufunga amashuri bishobora gutekerezwaho.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba guhura n'umuntu wanduye cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 basabwe gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abajyanama b'ubutabazi b'ibanze, harimo no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikwiye.
Niba imishyikirano ya hafi yabayeho mu gihe cyo gufata, abakozi bagomba gusukura no gukumira udukingirizo tw'imipira n'ibikoresho by'akazi mbere yo kongera kubikoresha bakoresheje isukari cyangwa impapuro zo gusukura mu rugo kandi bakurikize uburyo bwo gukora buzwi bwo kugenzura no gusana APD zishaje no kugenzura no gukaraba imyenda yanduye.
OSHA ibona ko bamwe mu bakozi bo mu bitaro n'abo mu nzu y'abapfuye bafite ibyago byo kwandura cyane.
Imirimo ishobora guteza ibyago byo kwandura cyane ni nko gutanga ubuvuzi, ubufasha, laboratwari, n'abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuvuzi n'ubwikorezi bw'ubwikorezi bw'abaganga bagaragaye cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye COVID-19.
Aka kazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi byo kwandura cyane cyane iyo umukozi ari gukora ku bikoresho byo guturitsa, cyangwa gutwara ibipimo ku barwayi b'abarwayi cyangwa abarwayi bakekwaho COVID-19.
Mu bikorwa byo gukora ibyuma bikoresha umwuka harimo gutwikira mu muhogo, kwinjiza mu muhogo, gukora isuzuma ry'ibihaha, bimwe mu bikorwa byo gusuzuma amenyo, cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'indwara z'umubiri.
Akaga gakomeye k'akazi k'ububiko kahumeka cyane harimo abakozi bakora mu gutegura intumbi z'abantu bazwi cyangwa bikekwa ko bafite COVID-19 igihe bapfuye; iyi mirimo iba yugarijwe cyane n'ibyago byo guhumeka iyo abakozi bakora autopsy. Ibindi by'ingenzi ku bari muri iyi itsinda ry'abafite ibyago harimo ibyumba by'ubwiherero ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bikekwaho COVID-19, harimo igihe hakorwa ibikorwa byo gukwirakwiza umwuka.
Imyanya y'umwuka w'umwuka mubi ishobora kuba ikwiriye mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuvuzi no mu byumba by'amaraso.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa mu buryo bw'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima bw'icyiciro cya 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryifuza ko abarwayi baza mu bitaro batandukanywa n'abari mu byumba bategeramo abantu bashinjwa COVID-19.Uretse izindi APD, OSHA isaba ko abantu bakora bari hagati y'ibirenge 6 by'abarwayi bazwiho cyangwa bikekwaho kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2, n'abantu bakora ibikorwa byo gukwirakwiza ibyuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka byo mu bwoko bwa N95 byemewe na NIOSH cyangwa biruta bigomba gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'igikorwa cyo kwandika no gukora porogaramu yo kurinda guhumeka, ikubiyemo gupima ubukana, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bwoko bw'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bishobora gutanga uburinzi bukomeye kandi bikongera ibidutunga. OMS ntiyemeza ko abantu bambara imyenda ifunganye cyangwa ikoti kuko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero kandi idandarizwa mu mazi.
OMS igaragaza ko udupfukamunwa two mu maso ari two gusa abantu bagomba kwambara igihe bari ku mupaka.
Ku bantu bafashe ibipimo byo mu buhumekero, bita ku barwayi cyangwa babajyana mu bitaro bya COVID-19 nta buryo bwo kubaha intungamubiri, OMS isaba ko bambara agapfukamunwa, amadarubindi, amakote n'utuntu tw'imbere.
Iyo habaho uburyo bwo guhumeka, agapfukamunwa gasimbuzwa agapfukamunwa ka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Dukurikije ko APD zitagikwiye ku isi hose, OMS irasaba kugabanya ibikenewe byose bya APD binyuze mu serivisi z'ubuvuzi bwa kure, imipaka y'umubiri nk'amadirishya y'amaso, hamwe n'abantu gusa bakora mu buryo butaziguye bemerewe kwinjira mu cyumba kirimo abarwayi ba COVID-19, gukoresha gusa APD zikenewe mu kazi runaka, gukomeza gukoresha respirator imwe udashyize hanze mu gihe ukorera abarwayi benshi bafite ibimenyetso bimwe, gukurikirana no guhuza umurongo wo gutanga APD, kandi ntugire inkunga yo gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
