Katherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jaime V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M, na Tony S), n'abandi bagize itsinda ry'ubuyobozi (Grant I, Heather W, Jaime V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M, na Toby N).
b'Enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ni enzymes zifata ku gice cyo hanze cy'ingirabuzima fatizo (membrane) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, umutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ifite imikorere inyuranye na angiotensin-ihindura enzymes (ACE), igabanya angiotensin-II kandi igatuma angiotensin (1-7) iba myinshi, bigatuma iba umuti wizewe wo kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'ahantu ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo kuri bamwe muri coronavirus.
ACE2 ubwoko bwa muntu burakunze kwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni metaloenzyme irimo zinc iboneka ku gice cyo hejuru cy'ingirabuzimafatizo (endothelial cell) ndetse no ku zindi ntangafatizo.
Poroteyine ACE2 ifite domaine M2 peptidase y'imperuka-N na domaine ya transporter ya acide aminal ya collectrin y'imperuka-C.
ACE2 ni poroteyine y'urwungano ya mbere y'ubwoko bumwe, ifite igice cy'ingenzi cy'imikorere ya poroteyine (domaine actif) igaragara ku isura y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
Icyiciro cya ACE2 cy'inyuma cyatandukanyijwe n'icyiciro cy'inyuma cy'ibindi byitwa sheddase, hanyuma poroteyine z'ibanze zikururwa mu mubiri zishyirwa mu maraso, amaherezo zikagaragara mu myanya y'ibanga.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifata ingingo z'umubiri cyane cyane iz'ibihaha by'ubwoko bwa II, intanga ntoya, intanga za endothelial z'amaraso n'amaraso, n'ingingo z'umubiri w'ingingo z'amaraso mu ngingo nyinshi.
Igaragaza rya mRNA ACE2 na ryo riboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, muri striatum, muri hypothalamus no mu nkingi z'ubwonko.
Inshingano y'ibanze ya ACE2 ni uko yahindura ACE.
ACE ituma angiotensin I ikora nk'uko angiotensin II ikora, bityo ikaba ari yo ikora mu mubiri.
Hanyuma, ACE2 igabanya amino acide ya phenylalanine karboksili iherezo rya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayishyira muri angiotensin (1-7) vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi gusenya ibindi bice by'umubiri birimo [des-Arg9] -bradikinine, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 nayo igenga ibinyabuzima byo mu mubiri byitwa SLC6A19 kandi ikaba ifite uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'imyororokere y'uruhu, ACE2 ni cyo cyerekezo cy'ibanze cy'inzira muri za mikorobe za koronavirusi, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV ( virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza kw'umwimerere wa S1 kuri SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 hamwe n'urwego rwa ACE2 ku isanzure ry'ingirabuzima bigira ingaruka zo gutura mu nda no kohereza virusi na enzymes muri endosome iri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi virusi kandi ikeneye ko protein S ya serine ya serine ya TMPRSS2 ikora priming, ubu ubu ubuzanyi bwaba bugenzurwa nk'uburyo bwo kuvura.
Ariko kandi, inzego nyinshi z'ubuvuzi n'iz'ubuyobozi zisaba ko hakomeza gukoreshwa imiti yo kuvura indwara ziterwa no kurwara kanseri yitwa ACE na ARB.
Isesengura ryihariye ryakozwe kandi ryasuzumwe, ryasohotse ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, ryagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byagabanutseho 34% by'ingaruka z'umurwayi wa pneumonia ugereranyije n'abagenzuzi".
Byongeye kandi, "gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo bigabanya ibyago byo guhumeka mu barwayi bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhumeka, cyane cyane abarwayi ba kanseri y'umutima n'abadafite umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo byashyizwe ku rwego rwo kugabanya impfu z'abantu bahuye n'impumyi, nubwo byagereranywa n'ibyago byo kurwara impumyi".
Igisubizo cy'umuntu cy'imiti ya ACE2 (rhACE2) giteganyijwe kuba uburyo bushya bwo kuvura imvune z'ubuhumekero, kandi bigaragara ko cyongera imikorere y'amaraso y'ubuhumekero n'umwuka wa oxygene mu bana b'ingurube bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ibikoresho bya lipoplisakaride.
Ikirengagizwa cy'ubuzima cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni hafi amasaha 10 n'igihe cy'akazi k'iminota 30 uretse ko igihe cy'ingaruka (duration) ari amasaha 24.
Bimwe mu byo yasanze bigaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku barwayi bafite intolerance ku nkingi z'ubuhumekero bwa RAS (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa ku barwayi bafite angiotensin II mu maraso.
porogaramu ya COVID-19 ni porogaramu ya mudasobwa igendanwa yagenewe gufasha gukurikirana abahuye nabo mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus cyo mu 2019-2020, ni ukuvuga, inzira yo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'abantu banduye.
Hari porogaramu nyinshi zikorwa cyangwa zashyizweho, kandi zigashyigikirwa na leta mu turere no mu nzego z'ubutegetsi.
Gahunda zitandukanye zo gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana abagenzi zarateguwe.
Ikibazo cy'ubuzima bwite bw'abantu kiracyekwa, cyane cyane ku bijyanye na sisitemu ishingiye ku gukurikirana ahantu abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Ibindi bisigaye by'ubuzima bw'umuntu burenze urugero harimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo byemeze ko umuntu ari hafi y'undi muntu.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bazakora ibikorwa byo gushyigikira porogaramu ya Bluetooth muri sisitemu ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'u Bushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu ifasha abaturage kureba niba barigeze guhura n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
Iyi porogaramu ikoreshwa mu mijyi n'utugari 200 mu Bushinwa.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo muri ako karere, yashyizwe ku mugaragaro kandi izajya ihabwa leta.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Ikoranabuhanga n'Itumanaho na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abahuye n'indwara iri mu bikorwa by'iterambere ryisumbuye kandi ko izatangira gukoreshwa mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyi irateganywa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na New Zealand barimo gutekereza ku porogaramu ishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapore na porogaramu ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite umugambi wo gutangiza porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi bapimweho COVID-19 baba i Moscow; iyi porogaramu yagenewe kwemeza ko batagiye mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ku bibazo by'ingirakamaro bishobora kubaho muri sisitemu ishingiye ku ikoreshwa ry'imikorere, harimo ibinyoma by'ibinyoma no kubura ubushobozi mu gihe amakuru ikoreshwa ry'imikorere yabitswe ku gice gito cy'abaturage.
Kugira ngo Apple itange igisubizo ku mpungenge z'impuruza y'imikorere ya "coronavirus" ishobora kuyobya cyangwa ikabangamira, yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora gushyira porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus kuri App Store, ni ukuvuga ko ishyiraho imipaka ku miryango "yemewe" cyangwa ifite izina ryiza.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho iyo mipaka.
Abashyigikiye ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'ingaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi hakoreshejwe porogaramu za coronavirus, cyane cyane niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubugenzuzi byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizakurwaho nyuma y'uko ibyago byashize.
Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakwirindwa ubu bushakashatsi.
Iryo shyirahamwe ryatanze ibisabwa umunani ku mushinga wa leta:
Ubugenzuzi bugomba kuba "bwemewe n'amategeko, bukenewe kandi buhuje n'urugero";
Ibipimo by'ubwirinzi n'ubugenzuzi bigomba kuba bifite itegeko ryo kurengera izuba;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba guhagarikwa gusa ku mpamvu za COVID-19;
Umutekano n'ubwisanzure bw'amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi bigakorwaho mu buryo bw'ibimenyetso;
Digital surveillance igomba kwirinda ivangura rikomeye no gushyirwa ku ruhande;
buri gusangira amakuru n'undi muntu wa gatatu bigomba gusobanurwa mu mategeko;
hagomba kubaho kurindwa ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo kwishinja ihohoterwa;
hakenewe uruhare rufite icyo rusobanura rw'abafatanyabikorwa bose, harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'imiryango y'abantu bari ku ngoyi.
Gahunda yashyizweho na Google na Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'igenzura ryihuta, ikuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana mu mikorere y'ibikoresho igihe bitagikenewe.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bikoresha uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari, aho gukoresha porogaramu, bityo bikuraho ko umuntu agomba gukuramo porogaramu no guhitamo uburyo bwo kwirinda gukurikiranwa.
Muri Isirayeli, uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu bukoresheje interineti bwemewe.
Igisubizo gishingiye ku muyoboro ugendana n'amakuru y'ahantu haboneka gishobora kuba gifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ubuzima bwite.
Ariko, sisitemu zose zifite seriveri rusange ntizikeneye kubona amakuru yihariye; sisitemu zimwe na zimwe zirinda ubuzima bwite zashyizweho kandi zikoresha seriveri rusange gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, uburyo butari bwo bwa porogaramu bukoreshwa mu gukurikirana abo bantu.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu zihariye, sisitemu ikusanya amakuru yo gukurikirana ituruka muburyo butandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibyuma bigendanwa hamwe namakuru yo kugurisha ikarita, hanyuma igahuza aya makuru kugirango itange ubutumwa bugufi kubwoherejwe.
Uretse gukoresha ayo makuru mu kuburira abantu bashobora kuba bahuye na bo, leta yashyize ayo makuru ku mugaragaro, nk'uko byari byemewe n'itegeko rigenga ibanga ry'amakuru ya bwite, nyuma y'uko igihugu cyibasiwe na MERS.
Amakuru agera kuri rubanda binyuze muri porogaramu zitandukanye no ku mbuga za interineti.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru arambuye ntabwo araboneka.
Kurikirana amatara arinda ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo cyashizweho, hamwe n'ibitabo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi kuva nibura mu 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi akora ku bisubizo by'ubuzima bwite, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE), kugirango bandike hafi y'abakoresha izindi telefoni.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni gahunda yo guhuza irimo uburyo bwibanze kandi bwimurwa, ntabwo ari porogaramu imwe. Porogaramu ya decentralized ikubiyemo Igereranyo ryibanze ryibanga ryibanga ryibanga (DP-PPT / DP-3T), Umubare wigihe gito (TCN, mbere yiswe Umubare w'ibanga ryibanga, CEN), Porogaramu n'uburyo bwihariye bw'ibanga ryibanga ryibanga ryibanga ry'imboneza (PACT), n'ibindi.
Muri aya mabwiriza, amakuru ashobora kumenyekana ku muntu n'umwe ntava ku gikoresho, kandi imikoranire yose iba ku gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'abantu bakora ibijyanye n'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab bakoze SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite mu gihe hakusanywa amakuru y'ahantu cyangwa aho amakuru ahurira kugira ngo hakurikiranwe icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ibi bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'igitabo cy'ubushakashatsi "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ubundi bushakashatsi nk'ubu ni urubuga rwa SafeTrace rwakozwe na Enigma MPC, isosiyete ikora mu bijyanye n'ibanga kandi ikaba yari isanzwe ikorera muri MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga rikoresha ibikoresho byabugenewe kugira ngo ikoreshe abantu bashobora gusangira amakuru y'aho baba n'amakuru y'ubuzima bwabo n'abandi bantu n'abashinzwe umutekano, ariko bitabangamiye ubuzima bwite bw'amakuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, Ihuriro mpuzamahanga rya TCN ryashinzwe n'amatsinda afite uburyo bumwe kandi ni porogaramu nyinshi zikwirakwizwa, hagamijwe kugabanya ibice no kwemerera ubufatanye ku isi hose ku bikorwa byo gukurikirana no kuburira, aribyo bintu by'ingenzi mu kugera ku kwemerwa kwa benshi.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yashyize ku mugaragaro BlueTrace ikoreshwa na porogaramu yemewe na guverinoma yayo.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenga kuri Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abagenzi, bavuga ko bizarinda ubuzima bwite, bishingiye ku guhuza ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy na cryptographie irinda ubuzima bwite.
Banashyize ahagaragara ibisobanuro birambuye by'ikoranabuhanga rikoreshwa muri iyo gahunda.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, iyi gahunda igomba gutangizwa mu byiciro bitatu:
