Muri Mata, ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya CEPI cyatangaje ko hari ikoranabuhanga 10 rigiye gukorwa mu ntangiriro za 2020 kugira ngo hakorwe urukingo rukwiye rwa COVID-19.
Intego z'ibanze z'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga byagezweho mu isuzuma ry'umutekano ryo mu cyiciro cya mbere, harimo:
nucleic acid (DNA na RNA) (bakangurambaga ba Phase I n'abakandida ba urukingo: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virusi (abakoze igice cya mbere n'umukandida w'urukingo: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus ya 5 y'ubwoko)
Nkuko byatangajwe n'abahanga muri siyansi ba CEPI mu kwezi kwa kane, umubare w'inkingo 115 ziri mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'iterambere, aho 78 zemejwe nk'imishinga ikora (79, nk'uko bivugwa n'ikigo cya Milken), naho indi 37 yatangajwe, ariko amakuru make cyane ari ku mugaragaro (bivugwa ko ari mu igenamigambi cyangwa ko ari mu bikorwa).
Icyiciro cya I-II cy'igerageza cy'ibanze gikora ku isuzuma ry'ubudahangarwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, akenshi mu buryo butunguranye, ku buryo butegekwa na placebo, no mu bibanza byinshi, mu gihe hagaragazwa igipimo cy'ubudahangarwa kizafasha mu buryo bukwiriye.
Ubusanzwe, ibizamini byo mu cyiciro cya III bikunze kuba ku bantu benshi, harimo n'itsinda ry'abashakashatsi, kandi bikagerageza kureba niba urukingo rufite ubushobozi bwo kurinda indwara, ari na ko rugenzura ingaruka mbi mu gihe rukoreshwa mu rugero rwiza.
